Wani kifi mai suna shark ya ji wa wani yaro ɗan shekara 13 rauni yayin da yake neman kwari a California
Wani kifi mai suna shark ya kai hari kuma ya ji rauni a ranar Asabar yayin da yaro dan shekara 13 ke yin ruwa don neman kwari a California a ranar farko ta kakar kwari, in ji hukumomi.
An kai harin ne kafin karfe 7 na safe a kusa da Beacon's Beach a Encinitas.
Chad Hammel ya shaida wa KSWB-TV a San Diego cewa ya shafe rabin sa'a yana ruwa tare da wasu abokai a safiyar Asabar lokacin da ya ji kukan wani yaro yana neman taimako.
Hammel ya ce da farko ya yi tunanin cewa farin ciki ne na kama wani lobster, amma sai ya gane cewa yana kuka 'An ciji ni!
Sun cije ni!'
Yana da dukan clavicle tsage, Hammel lura a lokacin da ya isa yaron.
"Saboda kowa ya fito daga cikin ruwan, sai na yi ihu, 'Akwai kifi a cikin ruwa!'", in ji Hammel.
An kai yaron zuwa asibitin Rady Children's Hospital na San Diego, inda aka kwantar da shi cikin mawuyacin hali.
Ba a san irin kifin da ke da alhakin harin ba.
A wani taron manema labarai, mai aikin ceto Larry Giles ya ce ya yi aiki a makonni da suka gabata cewa an gano wani kifi a yankin, amma an yanke shawarar cewa ba shi da haɗari.
Giles ya kara da cewa wanda aka kashe yana da raunuka a cikin babban ɓangaren jikinsa.
Hukumomi sun rufe tsawon awanni 48 daga Ponto Beach a Casablad zuwa Swami's a Ecinitas saboda binciken da kuma dalilai na tsaro.
Giles ya lura cewa akwai fiye da nau'in kifi 135 a yankin, amma yawancin su ba su da haɗari.
Shirye-shiryen Sainsbury's, zuwa kasuwar kayan kwalliyar Burtaniya
Sainsbury's ya yanke shawarar yin gasa da Boots, Superdrug da Debenhams tare da hanyoyin kayan kwalliya a cikin salon manyan shagunan da ke cike da ƙwararrun ma'aikata.
Waɗannan manyan hanyoyin ba su da yawa daga cikin manyan abubuwan da ake sakawa a cikin kasuwar kayan kwalliyar Burtaniya, kasuwar da ke motsawa kimanin fam biliyan 2.8, kuma tana ci gaba da ƙaruwa yayin da masana'antar kayan kwalliya da kayan gida ke baya, kuma za a gwada su a shaguna 11 a duk faɗin ƙasar don faɗaɗa zuwa ƙarin shaguna a shekara mai zuwa idan gwajin ya ci nasara.
Zuba jari a cikin kayan kwalliya ya samo asali ne daga kwaɗayin manyan kantuna don amfani da sararin samaniya a kan ɗakunan ajiyar su wanda a baya aka yi amfani da shi don talabijin, microwaves da kayayyakin gida.
Sainsbury's ya ce zai ninka kyautar kayan kwalliyarsa don samar da kayayyaki daban-daban har zuwa 3,000, gami da a karon farko alamun kamar Revlon, Essie, Tweezerman da Dr. PawPaw.
L L L'Oreal, Maybelline da Burt's Bees sun riga sun sami ƙarin sarari tare da yankuna masu kama da waɗanda za a iya samu a shaguna kamar Boots.
Kamfanin kantin sayar da kayayyaki yana cikin sake ƙaddamar da kewayon kayan kwalliyar Boutique don yawancin samfuran yanzu sun dace da vegan, wani abu da matasa masu amfani ke buƙata.
Shagon sayar da kayayyaki The Fragrance Shop, zai kuma buɗe kaya a shagunan Sainsbury's biyu. Na farko ya yi hakan a makon da ya gabata a Croydon, a kudancin Landan, yayin da na biyu zai buɗe a Selly Oak, Birmingham, a ƙarshen wannan shekarar.
Kasuwancin kan layi da kuma sauyawa zuwa al'adar sayen abinci a cikin ƙananan ƙananan kaya a kowace rana a ƙananan kantuna sun sa manyan kantuna su nemi wasu hanyoyin da za su sa mutane su zo.
A cewar Mike Coupe, babban daraktan kamfanin Sainsbury's, shagunan za su zama kamar manyan kantuna a ƙoƙarin da babbar kasuwar ke yi na yin yaƙi da manyan kantunan ragi Aldi da Lidl tare da ƙarin sabis da kayayyakin da ba abinci ba.
Sainsbury's ya gabatar da wuraren sayar da Argos a yawancin manyan kantunansa, ban da wasu shagunan Habitat tun lokacin da ya sayi duka sarƙoƙi biyu shekaru biyu da suka gabata, wanda, in ji shi, ya taimaka wajen sake dawo da tallace-tallace na kayan abinci da haɓaka ribar sayan.
Ƙoƙarin da aka yi a baya na babban kanti don sake dawo da sassan kayan ado da kantin magani ya zama rashin nasara.
Sainsbury's ya yi gwajin aiki tare da Boots a farkon shekarun 2000, amma duk ya ƙare da sauri ba tare da yarda da yadda za a raba ribar da ke cikin kantin magani a cikin manyan kantuna ba.
Wannan sabon dabarun ya biyo bayan sayar da kasuwancin Sainsbury's na kantin magani 281 zuwa Celesio, mai mallakar sarkar LloydsPharmacy, shekaru uku da suka gabata don GBP 125 miliyan.
A cewar Sainsbury's, Lloyds zai taka muhimmiyar rawa a cikin shirin duniya, saboda zai faɗaɗa kewayon samfuran samfuran fata masu daraja, kamar La Roche-Posay ko Vichy, zuwa shaguna huɗu.
Paul Mills-Hicks, babban jami'in kasuwanci na Sainsbury's ya ce: "Mun canza yadda kayan kwalliyarmu ke tafiya don inganta yanayin da ke gaban abokan cinikinmu.
Mun saka hannun jari a cikin ma'aikatan da aka horar da su musamman waɗanda za su taimaka sosai wajen ba da shawara.
An tsara samfuranmu don dacewa da kowane buƙata; a gefe guda, yanayin da ke da kyau da wuri mai dacewa ya sa yanzu mun zama ɗaya daga cikin wuraren da aka fi so don kayan kwalliya da ƙalubalanci hanyar cin kasuwa ta gargajiya.
Peter Jones fushi bayan Holly Willoughby ya yi baya a kan yarjejeniyar £11 miliyan
Tauraron Dragons' Den Peter Jones ya tafi furious bayan mai gabatar da shirye-shiryen talabijin Holly Willoughby ta bi bayan yarjejeniyar £ 11 miliyan tare da kasuwancin kasuwancin Jones don mayar da hankali kan sabbin kwangilarsa tare da Marks da Spencer da ITV.
Willoughby ba shi da lokacin da zai ba da kansa ga kasuwancin gida da kayan haɗi na Truly.
Kasuwancin waɗannan mutane biyu na kafofin watsa labarai sun kasance suna kwatanta su da alamar Gwyneth Paltrow ta Goop.
Mai gabatar da wannan safiyar, mai shekaru 37, ta yi amfani da Instagram don sanar da tafiyarta.
Holly Willoughby ta sa tauraron Dragons 'Den Peter Jones ya fusata da janyewa a minti na karshe daga kasuwancin haɗin gwiwar salon rayuwa mai riba don mai da hankali kan sabbin kwangilarsa tare da Marks & Spencer da ITV, wanda zai kawo masa babbar riba.
A cewar wasu majiyoyi, Jones ya kasance furious lokacin da tauraron talabijin ya yarda, yayin taron da aka yi a ranar Talata a hedkwatar mulkinsa a Marlow, Buckinghamshire, cewa sabbin yarjejeniyar mai gabatarwar, wanda ya kai dala miliyan 1.5 , ya nuna cewa ba za ta sami isasshen lokaci ba don sadaukar da ita ga haɗin gwiwar kayan gida da kayan haɗi na Truly.
An kwatanta kasuwancin da Gwyneth Paltrow Goop kuma yana son ninka dukiyar Willoughby, wanda aka kiyasta a miliyan 11 GBP.
Lokacin da Willoughby, mai shekaru 37, ya yi amfani da Instagram don sanar da tafiyarsa daga Truly, Jones ya ɗauki jirgin sama mai zaman kansa zuwa ɗaya daga cikin wuraren hutunsu a waje da Burtaniya.
A cewar wata majiya:  Truly ta kasance mafi mahimmancin Holly.
Wannan shi ne abin da zai kasance a gaba a cikin shekaru 20 zuwa 30 masu zuwa.
Amma, shawarar da ya tsai da ta sa dukan waɗanda suka yi hakan suka yi mamaki.
Babu wanda ya yarda da abin da ya faru a ranar Talata, mun kasance kusa da kaddamarwa...
A yanzu haka akwai babban kantin sayar da kayayyaki a hedkwatar Marlow a shirye don sayarwa.
A cewar masana, barin mai gabatar da wannan safiya, ɗaya daga cikin taurari masu fa'ida a Burtaniya, na iya biyan kamfanin miliyoyin saboda babban saka hannun jari da aka yi a cikin kayayyaki, daga matashin kai da kyandirori zuwa tufafi da tufafi don gida, da yiwuwar jinkiri don ƙaddamar da shi.
Ƙari ga haka, zai iya kawo ƙarshen abokantaka mai kyau.
Willoughby, mahaifiyar yara uku, da mijinta Dan Baldwin sun kasance suna da dangantaka mai kyau da Jones da matarsa Tara Capp har tsawon shekaru goma.
Willoughby ya kafa Truly tare da Capp a shekara ta 2016, kuma Jones, mai shekaru 52, ya shiga shi a matsayin shugaban a watan Maris da ya gabata.
Dukansu ma'aurata suna yin hutu tare. Bugu da ƙari, Jones yana da kashi 40 cikin dari na hannun jari a kamfanin talabijin na Baldwin.
Willoughby za ta zama jakada ta gaba ta M&S kuma za ta maye gurbin Ant McPartlin a matsayin mai gabatar da shirin ITV na I'm A Celebrity.
Wata majiya da ke kusa da Jones ta ce a daren jiya ba za mu yi wani bayani game da harkokin kasuwancinsa ba.
