Lura: Daniel Sturridge na Liverpool ya zira kwallo a wasan da aka tashi daga baya a Chelsea
Daniel Sturridge ya ceci Liverpool daga shan kashi a gasar Premier da Chelsea tare da burinsa a minti na 89 a ranar Asabar a Stamford Bridge, London.
Sturridge ya samu wata hanya daga Xherdan Shaqiri a kimanin mita 27 daga ƙofar Chelsea lokacin da tawagarsa ta rasa 1-0.
Ya juya kwallon zuwa hagu kafin ya saki wani harbi mai ban mamaki zuwa ga na biyu.
Harbin ya ratsa yankin gaba daya tare da babban tashin hankali yayin da yake motsawa zuwa ga madaidaicin ƙofar ƙofar.
Daga ƙarshe kwallon ta fara saukowa sama da Kepa Arrizabalaga a cikin tsalle don ƙoƙarin dakatar da ita kuma ta ƙare a ƙasan raga.
Na yi ƙoƙari ne kawai in isa wannan matsayin don in iya harba, kuma 'yan wasa kamar Shaqiri koyaushe suna yin gaba gaba da yadda zai yiwu, don haka na yi ƙoƙarin ƙirƙirar lokaci mai yawa yadda zan iya, in ji Sturridge a LiverpoolFC.com.
Na ga Kanté yana zuwa, na yi wasa kuma ban yi tunani sosai ba, kawai na ba da kaina ga wasa.
Chelsea ta ci 1-0 a hutu bayan ta ci kwallo a minti na 25 ta hannun tauraron Belgian Eden Hazard.
A cikin wasan, dan wasan gaba na kungiyar Blue ya dawo da kafa a kan Mateo Kovacic kafin ya tashi daga kusan rabin filin wasa kuma ya shiga filin Liverpool.
Kovacic ya yi haɗuwa da sauri daga tsakiyar filin wasa.
Bayan haka, ya yi kyakkyawar tafiya mai zurfi, wanda ya bar Hazard a cikin yankin tare da kula da kwallon.
Hazard ya shawo kan tsaron don kammala a filin wasa na biyu tare da bugun ƙafar hagu inda mai tsaron Liverpool Alisson Becker bai iya isa ba.
Liverpool za ta fafata da Napoli a wasan rukuni na gasar zakarun Turai a ranar Laraba da ke tafe da karfe 3:00 na dare a filin wasa na Stadio San Paolo da ke Naples, Italiya.
Chelsea, a gefe guda, za ta buga wasan Videoton a gasar UEFA Europa League ranar Alhamis da karfe 15:00 a London.
