Sama da mutane miliyan 20 ne suka kalli jawabin Brett Kavanaugh
Sama da mutane miliyan 20 ne suka kalli shaidar mai cike da sha'awa da aka bayar a ranar Alhamis ta wanda zai zama babban alkalin kotun koli Brett Kavanaugh da matar da ta zarge shi da cin zarafin mata, Christine Blasey Ford, wanda ake zargin ya faru ne a shekarun 1980s.
A halin yanzu, rikicin siyasa ya ci gaba, tare da tashoshin watsa labarai suna katse shirye-shiryen Juma'a na yau da kullun saboda juyin halitta na minti na ƙarshe: yarjejeniyar da Sanata Jeff Flake na Arizona ya tsara don FBI ta gudanar da binciken zargin na mako guda.
Ford ta bayyana wa Kwamitin Shari'a na Majalisar Dattawa cewa ta tabbata cewa Kavanaugh ya taɓa ta da giya kuma ya yi ƙoƙari ya cire tufafinta a wani biki a makarantar sakandare.
Kavanaugh, a cikin shaidar da ya yi, ya ce ya tabbata cewa hakan bai faru ba.
A cewar Nielsen, mai yiwuwa fiye da masu kallo miliyan 20.4 ne suka kalli wannan shaida a ranar Juma'a.
Kamfanin ya ƙidaya matsakaicin masu kallo na tashoshin CBS, ABC, NBC, CNN, Fox News Channel da MSNBC.
Ba a sami lambobin masu sauraro nan da nan ta sauran tashoshin da suka sake watsa shaidar ba, kamar PBS, C-SPAN ko Fox Business Network.
Ƙari ga haka, Nielsen yana yawan samun matsala wajen lissafin yawan mutanen da suke kallon bidiyon daga ofishinsa.
Idan aka mai da shi ga hangen nesa, wannan yana kama da kallon wasan ƙwallon ƙafa ko bikin Oscar.
Fox News Channel, wanda shugabannin ra'ayoyinsa suka ba da goyon baya ga nadin Kavanaugh, shine tashar da ta fi sauraro, tare da matsakaicin masu kallo miliyan 5.69 a duk lokacin da ake shaidawa a rana, a cewar Nielsen.
ABC ta kasance ta biyu tare da masu kallo miliyan 3.26.
CBS ta samu miliyan 3.1 da NBC miliyan 2.94, MSNBC miliyan 2.89 da CNN miliyan 2.52, a cewar bayanan Nielsen.
Ba a taɓa samun irin wannan sha'awar ba bayan shaidar.
Flake ne babban jigon wasan kwaikwayo na Jumma'a.
Bayan ofishin Jamhuriyar Republican ya ba da sanarwar cewa za su kada kuri'ar Kavanaugh, Flake ya kama kyamarorin CNN da CBS a safiyar ranar Juma'a yayin da masu zanga-zanga ke tayar da shi yayin da yake ƙoƙarin hawa lif don halartar taron Kwamitin Shari'a.
Flake ya kasance da ido a cikin minti da yawa yayin da aka sake buga shi kai tsaye a talabijin a CNN.
"Ga ni a gabanka", wata mata ta ce.
Kuna tsammanin yana faɗin gaskiya ga ƙasar?
Sun ce mata 'kana da iko, alhali akwai mata da yawa da ba su da shi!
Flake ya ce ofishinsa ya ba da sanarwa kuma kafin a rufe ƙofofin lif ɗin, ya ce yana da ƙarin abin da zai faɗa a gaban kwamitin.
A cikin 'yan sa'o'i, dukkan tashoshin talabijin da na talabijin sun fara watsa shirye-shiryen da ke nuna lokacin da Kwamitin Shari'a ya yanke shawarar ko ya ci gaba da nadin Kavanaugh a majalisar dattijai don jefa kuri'a.
Flake ya ce, a maimakon haka, zai yi hakan ne kawai da sanin cewa FBI za ta binciki zargin da ake yi wa wanda aka zaba a mako mai zuwa, yanayin da 'yan Democrat suka bukaci.
Flake ya yarda da shi a wani ɓangare saboda tattaunawar da ya yi da abokinsa, Sanata Chris Coons na Democrat.
Bayan tattaunawa da Coons da wasu sanatoci, Flake ya yanke shawarar.
Zaɓin da Flake ya zaɓa yana da tasiri, saboda a bayyane yake cewa 'yan Republican ba za su sami isasshen kuri'u don tallafawa Kavanaugh ba tare da binciken ba.
Shugaba Trump ya bude binciken FBI kan zargin da ake yi wa Kavanaugh.
Firaministar Birtaniya May ta zargi masu sukar ta da 'yin siyasa' game da Brexit
Firayim Minista Theresa May ta zargi masu sukar shirin ta na barin Tarayyar Turai da "yin siyasa" da makomar Burtaniya da kuma raina bukatun kasa a wata hira da jaridar Sunday Times.
Firayim Ministan Burtaniya Theresa May ta isa taron jam'iyyar Conservative a Birmingham, Burtaniya, 29 ga Satumba, 2018.
A wata hira da aka yi da May a shafin jaridar, tsohon ministan harkokin wajen May Boris Johnson ya kara kaiwa harin da ake kira shirin Chequers na Brexit, inda ya ce shawarar da Birtaniya da EU ke yi na karbar haraji daga juna  abin dariya ne .
'Yan sanda sun kama wani mutum mai suna Dyteon Simpson a kan laifin kisan dan wasan LSU
'Yan sanda sun kama wani da ake zargi da harin Wayde Sims, dan wasan kwando mai shekaru 20 da haihuwa wanda ke taka leda a LSU.
An kama Dyteon Simpson, mai shekara 20, kuma an daure shi a kurkuku bisa laifin kisan kai na biyu, in ji 'yan sanda a Baton Rouge.
Hukumomi sun saki bidiyon da aka yi tsakanin Sims da Simpson.
'Yan sanda sun dawo da tabarau a wurin kisan kuma sun ce sun sami DNA na Simpson a cikinsu, in ji CBS affiliate WAFB.
Bayan ya yi wa Simpson tambayoyi, ya yarda da kashe Wayde da harbi, in ji 'yan sanda.
An saka kudin belinsa a kan dala 350,000, in ji lauyan.
Ofishin kula da lafiyar mutane na yankin East Baton Rouge ya fitar da rahoto na farko a ranar Juma'a, inda ya ce dalilin mutuwar shi ne harbin bindiga a kai da aka yi wa wuyansa.
Ma'aikatar ta gode wa rundunar 'yan sanda na jihar Louisiana, da 'yan sanda na jihar, da jami'an 'yan sanda na Jami'ar Southern da kuma mazauna yankin don taimakon da suka bayar a binciken da ya kai ga wannan kama.
Daraktan wasanni na LSU Joe Alleva ya nuna godiyarsa ga jami'an tsaro na yankin saboda ƙwazo da kuma neman adalci.
Sims yana da shekaru 20.
Matsayin 1.98 m, ya taka leda a kan gaba kuma ya girma a Baton Rouge, inda mahaifinsa, Wayne, ya kasance dan wasan kwando a LSU.
Ya yi kimanin 5.6 da 2.6 rebounds a kakar wasa ta ƙarshe.
A safiyar ranar Juma'a, kocin kwando na LSU Will Wade ya yi sharhi cewa ƙungiyar ta "ruguje" kuma mutuwar Wayde ta kasance "mai ƙarfi sosai".
"Abubuwa irin wannan ne ke sa ka wahala a kowane lokaci", in ji Wade.
Wani dutsen mai fitad da wuta a birnin Mexico
Ƙurar da dutsen Popocatepetl ya zubar ta kai unguwar kudancin babban birnin Mexico.
Cibiyar rigakafin bala'i ta kasar ta gargadi 'yan Mexico a ranar Asabar da su guji volcano bayan da aka gano aiki a cikin ramin kuma an yi rikodin fitar da gas 183 da toka a cikin awa 24.
Cibiyar ta lura da wasu abubuwa da suka faru a baya-bayan nan.
Hotunan da aka yada a shafukan sada zumunta inda ake ganin wasu manyan laka a kan gilashin mota a unguwannin Mexico City kamar Xochimilco.
Masana ilimin kasa sun gano karuwar ayyukan dutsen mai fitad da wuta wanda ke da nisan kilomita 72 kudu maso gabashin babban birnin kasar tun lokacin da girgizar kasa mai karfin awo 7.1 ta girgiza tsakiyar Mexico a watan Satumbar 2017.
Dutsen mai fitad da wuta, wanda aka sani da sunan Don Goyo, ya ci gaba da aiki tun daga 1994.
'Yan sanda sun yi arangama da 'yan 'yan adawar Catalonia kafin ranar tunawa da zaben raba gardama kan 'yancin kai
An kama mutane shida a Barcelona a ranar Asabar bayan da masu zanga-zangar neman 'yancin kai suka yi arangama da 'yan sanda masu zanga-zanga da dubban mutane suka yi a zanga-zangar nuna rashin amincewarsu don tunawa da ranar farko da aka yi zaben raba gari a Catalonia.
Wasu 'yan gwagwarmayar neman' yancin kai da 'yan sanda suka kama sun fara jefa ƙwai da fenti a cikin kura, wanda ya haifar da bayyanar girgije mai duhu a kan titunan da yawanci masu yawon bude ido ke mamayewa.
Daga baya a ranar, an yi arangama da 'yan sanda, wadanda suka yi amfani da sandunansu don dakile masu zanga-zangar.
A cikin sa'o'i da yawa, ƙungiyoyin 'yancin kai suna rera waƙa Ba za mu manta ba, ba za mu gafarta ba fuska da fuska tare da masu zanga-zangar ƙungiyar da ke ihu Long life in Spain.
Mutane 14 sun samu raunuka a lokacin zanga-zangar, a cewar majiyoyin yankin.
Matsaloli ba su ragu a wannan yanki mai neman 'yancin kai ba shekara guda bayan da aka gudanar da kuri'ar raba gardama a ranar 1 ga Oktoba da Madrid ta yi la'akari da doka amma har yanzu 'yan 'yan adawar Catalonia ne suka gudanar da ita.
Masu jefa kuri'a sun zaɓi 'yancin kai da yawa, kodayake ƙimar halartar ta yi ƙasa, saboda waɗanda ke adawa da raba gari sun fi yawan ƙin jefa kuri'a.
A cewar hukumomin Catalonia, kusan mutane 1000 ne suka ji rauni a bara bayan da 'yan sanda suka yi kokarin dakatar da zaben ta hanyar shiga wuraren zabe a duk yankin, lamarin da ya haifar da rikici.
Kungiyoyin 'yancin kai sun yi zango a daren Juma'a don hana zanga-zangar nuna goyon baya ga 'yan sanda.
An gudanar da zanga-zangar duk da haka, amma an tilasta masu zanga-zangar su bi wata hanya.
Narcís Termes, mai aikin lantarki mai shekaru 68 da daya daga cikin masu halartar zanga-zangar neman 'yancin kai tare da matarsa, ya ce ba shi da bege game da yiwuwar Catalonia ta samu 'yancin kai.
A shekarar da ta shige, mun yi farin ciki sosai.
Na ga iyayena suna kuka saboda farin ciki da samun damar jefa kuri'a, amma yanzu mun makale, in ji ta.
Duk da samun gagarumar nasara, ko da yake ta hanyar kaɗan, a zaɓen yankin a watan Disamba da ya gabata, jam'iyyun 'yancin kai na Catalonia sun sha wahala don ci gaba da ci gaba a wannan shekara, yayin da yawancin manyan shugabanninsu ke gudun hijira ko kuma an tsare su suna jiran a yi musu hukunci saboda rawar da suka taka wajen shirya kuri'ar raba gardama da kuma sanar da 'yancin kai.
Joan Puig, wani mai aikin injiniya mai shekaru 42, ya yi rikodin zanga-zangar goyon bayan 'yan sanda da wayarsa, kuma ya ce 'yan siyasa daga bangarorin biyu ne suka tayar da rikici.
