Wani wasa da Menga ya yi ya ba Livingston nasara 1-0 a kan Rangers
Dolly Menga ta fara cin kwallo a wasan Livingston kuma ta lashe gasar
Livingston, wanda ya hau kan sa a wannan shekara, ya ba Glasgow Rangers mamaki a abin da kawai shine kashi na biyu na Steven Gerrard a wasanni 18 a matsayin kocin ƙungiyar unguwar Ibrox.
Dolly Menga ta yi wasa ta nuna bambanci, saboda, tare da wannan nasarar, ƙungiyar Gary Holt ta hau zuwa matsayi na biyu, wanda suke rabawa tare da Hibernian.
A ranar Lahadi mai zuwa, za su fuskanci Hearts, wanda ke da maki takwas.
Amma kafin wannan, Rangers za su karbi Rapid na Vienna a gasar Europa League a wannan Alhamis.
Livingston, a halin yanzu, ta faɗaɗa zuwa wasanni shida da ba ta ci nasara a gasar ba, tare da Holt a matsayin kocin da har yanzu bai san abin da rashin nasara yake ba tun lokacin da ya maye gurbin Kenny Miler a watan da ya gabata.
Livingston ba ta amfani da damar da ta samu a gaban 'yan wasa masu zuwa
Ya kamata ƙungiyar Holt ta kasance a gaban maki kafin a ci kwallo, saboda wasan da ya yi kai tsaye ya haifar da matsaloli iri-iri a Rangers.
Scott Robinson ya yi tsalle a cikin tsaro, amma ya ɓata damarsa lokacin da ya sami kansa a gaban mai tsaron gida. Bayan haka, Alan Lithgow ya aika da kwallon a waje a kan shimfiɗa don ƙoƙarin rufe ƙofar Craig Halkett, wanda ya ƙetare ƙofar.
Masu gida sun riga sun yarda da barin Rangers su kusanci yankin su, saboda sun san cewa za su iya sa baƙi cikin matsala a cikin wasanni masu zaman kansu.
Kuma wannan shine yadda wannan burin ya zo.
Alkalin wasa ya yi wa Rangers laifi kuma Livingston ya buɗe wa band, inda Declan Gallagher da Robinson suka haɗu don Menga ya fara buga shi kuma ya gama daga tsakiyar yankin.
Har zuwa wannan lokacin, Rangers sun mamaye mallakar, amma sun sami kariya mai ƙarfi da mai tsaron gida Liam Kelly wanda ke da ɗan aiki a cikin wasan,
An sake maimaita wannan yanayin a kashi na biyu, duk da cewa Alfredo Morelos ya tilasta wa Kelly ya yi tsayayya da cancanta.
A gefe guda kuma, mai tsaron gidan Rangers Allan McGregor ya dakatar da ƙafafunsa a kan Scott Pittman kuma Lithgow ya kammala wani wasa na Livingston.
Rangers sun yi ƙoƙari su rataye sau ɗaya da sauran ƙwallon ƙafa a yankin Livingston, kawai don a ƙi su. Bugu da ƙari, an nemi hukuncin kisa guda biyu, ɗaya don zargin Halkett a cikin Glenn Middleton, da kuma wani don hannayensu.
