An yi wa Erdogan maraba da farin ciki a Cologne
Duk abin murmushi ne da sararin sama a ranar Asabar (29 ga Satumba) lokacin da shugabannin Turkiyya da Jamus suka taru don cin abincin rana a Berlin.
Ranar farko ce ta ziyarar da shugaba Erdogan ya kai Jamus, wanda ya yi niyyar gyara dangantaka tsakanin kasashen biyu da ke kawance da NATO.
Waɗannan sun lalace saboda batutuwan kamar haƙƙin ɗan adam, 'yancin' yan jarida da shiga Turkiyya cikin EU.
Erdogan ya koma Cologne don buɗe sabon babban masallaci.
Kuma wannan birni yana da mafi yawan mutanen Turkiyya a duniya a waje da Turkiyya.
'Yan sanda sun yi ikirarin dalilai na tsaro don hana taron mutane 25,000 taruwa a gaban masallacin, kodayake yawancin magoya bayansa sun taru a kusa da su don ganin shugabanta.
Daruruwan masu zanga-zangar adawa da Erdogan, da yawa daga cikinsu Kurdawa, sun yi magana yayin da suke la'antar manufofin Erdogan da kuma shawarar da gwamnatin Jamus ta yanke na maraba da shi a kasar.
Duk waɗannan zanga-zangar suna nuna rarrabuwar kawuna da ke kewaye da baƙon, wanda wasu Turkawa na Jamus ke ɗaukarsa gwarzo kuma wasu ke ɗaukarsa mai mulkin kama karya.
Hadarin mota a Deptford: mai hawan keke ya mutu bayan ya yi karo da mota
