Direban motar ya tsaya kuma, kodayake sabis na paramedic sun kula da mai hawan keke, ya mutu a kan aikin.
Hadarin ya zo ne watanni bayan da wani mai hawan keke ya mutu a wani hatsari da ya faru a Childers Street, kilomita daya daga wurin hatsarin ranar Asabar.
'Yan sanda sun ce jami'an su na kokarin gano mutumin da kuma sanar da danginsa.
An rufe titin kuma an yi amfani da hanyoyi don zirga-zirgar bas kuma an shawarci direbobi da su guji yankin.
An ji wa jami'an 'yan sanda shida rauni a wata rikici a gidan yarin Long Lartin
Jami'an gidan yarin sun jikkata mutane shida a wani rikici a gidan yarin da ke da tsaron tsaro, a cewar ofishin gidan yarin.
An yi wannan abu ne a gidan yarin Long Lartin, Worcestershire, da misalin karfe 9:30 na ranar Lahadi, agogon yankin, kuma har yanzu yana ci gaba.
Jami'an tornado na musamman sun tafi wurin da lamarin ya faru don kawo karshen rikici, wanda fursunoni takwas suka shiga ciki.
An yi wa jami'an asibiti magani saboda raunuka a fuskokinsu a wurin da aka yi kisan.
A cewar wani kakakin hukumar, "Mun tura ma'aikatan gidan yari da aka horar da su musamman don magance wani abin da ya faru a gidan yarin Long Martin, wanda har yanzu yana ci gaba.
An yi wa ma'aikata shida jinya don raunuka.
Ba za mu yarda da tashin hankali a gidajen yarinmu ba, kuma mun san cewa waɗanda suka yi wannan tashin hankali za su amsa wa 'yan sanda kuma za su iya yin ƙarin lokaci a kurkuku.
Gidan kurkuku na Long Lartin yana ɗauke da fursunoni fiye da 500, har da wasu masu laifi masu haɗari.
A watan Yuni, an sanar da cewa an kai shugaban gidan yari asibiti bayan wani fursuna ya kai masa hari.
Bugu da ƙari, a watan Oktoba na bara, jami'an tsaro sun halarci kurkuku don magance rikici mai tsanani inda ma'aikatan cibiyar suka kai hari da kwallon pool.
Guguwar Rosa ta yi barazanar Phoenix, Las Vegas da Salt Lake City da manyan ambaliyar ruwa (yankuna na iya amfana)
Ba a saba ganin wani yanayi mai zafi a Arizona, amma wannan shi ne abin da zai faru a farkon mako mai zuwa lokacin da sauran guguwar Rosa ta wuce cikin hamadar kudu maso yamma, tare da haɗarin ambaliyar ruwa.
Hukumar Kula da Yanayi ta Kasa ta ba da gargaɗin guguwa a ranar Litinin da Talata a yammacin Arizona zuwa kudu da gabashin Nevada, kudu maso gabashin California da Utah, ciki har da biranen Phoenix, Flagstaff, Las Vegas da Salt Lake City.
Ana sa ran guguwar Rosa za ta kai Phoenix a ranar Talata kuma za ta yi ruwan sama a ranar Litinin.
Sabis na National Weather Service na Phoenix ya yi sharhi a cikin wani rahoto cewa kawai guguwa goma sha biyu sun ci gaba da kasancewa a cikin hadari ko yanayin damuwa a cikin radius na 322 km na Phoenix tun 1950.
Guguwar Katrina (1967) ta tsaya kilomita 64 daga iyakar Arizona.
Sabbin samfuran cibiyar guguwa ta ƙasa suna hasashen ruwan sama na 50 zuwa 100 mm, tare da wuraren da aka ware inda za a yi rikodin har zuwa 150 mm a Mogollon na Arizona.
Sauran yankunan hamada na kudu maso yamma, ciki har da Rocky Mountains da kuma Great Basin, na iya yin rikodin 25 zuwa 50 mm, tare da yiwuwar wuraren da ke da iyaka har zuwa 100 mm.
Ga yankunan da ba su da haɗarin ambaliyar ruwa, ruwan sama na Rosa zai iya zama labari mai kyau, saboda yankin yana fama da fari mai tsanani.
Ko da yake ambaliyar ruwa tana da tsanani, amma wasu ruwan sama za su iya zama da amfani sosai, tun da yake yankin kudu maso yammacin ƙasar yana fama da fari.
A cewar Hukumar Kula da Fari ta Amirka, fiye da kashi 40 cikin ɗari na jihar Arizona suna fama da matsanancin fari, wato, kashi na biyu mafi girma, in ji weather.com.
Amma da farko, guguwar Rosa za ta sauka a yankin Baja California, a ƙasar Mexico.
Rosa ya ci gaba da samun ƙarfin guguwa a safiyar Lahadi, tare da iskar da ta kai kilomita 137 a kowace awa, kuma yanzu tana da nisan mil 620 daga kudu na Punta Eugenia, Mexico, tana tafiya zuwa arewa da sauri kilomita 20 a kowace awa.
Guguwar ta sami ruwan sanyi a cikin Pacific, wanda ke sa ta rasa ƙarfi.
Saboda haka, ana sa ran zai sauka a Mexico a matsayin guguwa mai karfi da yamma ko yammacin Litinin.
Ruwan sama a sassa daban-daban na Mexico na iya zama mai ƙarfi, tare da haɗarin ambaliyar ruwa mai yawa.
A cewar weather.com, ana tsammanin ruwan sama na 75 zuwa 150 mm daga Baja California zuwa arewa maso yammacin Sonora, tare da yiwuwar kaiwa 250 mm.
Bayan haka, Rosa za ta yi tafiya zuwa arewa ta hanyar Mexico tare da ƙarfin guguwa mai zafi, kafin ta isa iyakar Arizona da sanyin safiya na ranar Talata tare da ƙarfin damuwa mai zafi, don ƙarshe ta ƙetare jihar Arizona kuma ta isa kudancin Utah da yammacin ranar Talata.
Babban haɗarin da muke tsammanin daga Rosa ko abin da ya rage daga gare shi shine ruwan sama mai yawa a Baja California, arewa maso yammacin Sonora da hamadar kudu maso yammacin Amurka, a cewar cibiyar guguwa ta kasa.
Ana tsammanin ruwan sama zai haifar da kogi masu haɗari da kwararar shara a cikin hamada, ban da lalata ƙasa a yankunan tsaunuka.
An kama mutane hudu da laifin kisan kai a Midsomer Norton
An kama wasu matasa uku da wani mutum mai shekaru 20 a kan zargin yunkurin kisan kai bayan da aka samu wani yaro mai shekaru 16 da hannu a Somerset.
An gano matashin da raunuka a yankin Excelsior Terrace na Midsomer Norton, da misalin karfe 4:00 na ranar Asabar, agogon yankin.
