Trump ya ce Kavanaugh ya sha wahala daga rashin hankali da fushin jam'iyyar Democrat
"Zabe na ga Alkali Kavanaugh ya nuna rashin amincewa da mummunan aiki da kuma rashin jin daɗin jam'iyyar Democrat", in ji Trump a wani taron zaɓe a Wheeling, West Virginia.
Trump ya ce Kavanaugh ya "sha wahala daga ƙazanta da fushi" na jam'iyyar Democrat a duk lokacin da aka nada shi.
Kavanaugh ya shaida wa majalisa a ranar Alhamis, yana musun zargin Christine Blasey Ford na cin zarafinta shekaru da yawa da suka wuce, lokacin da suke matashi.
Ford kuma ya shaida a gaban kotu game da wanda ake tuhuma.
Shugaban ya ce a ranar Asabar cewa, a wannan ranar, "Mutanen Amurka sun ga basirar, ingancin ɗan adam da ƙarfin hali" na Kavanaugh.
"Zaɓen da aka yi na tabbatar da shari'ar Kavanaugh, na tabbatar da ɗaya daga cikin manyan masu shari'ar zamaninmu, lauya mai kyakkyawan tarihin aiki ga jama'a", in ji shi a gaban jama'ar da ke zaune a West Virginia.
Shugaban ya ambaci nadin Kavanaugh a kaikaice yayin da yake magana game da mahimmancin ƙididdigar ƙuri'ar masu jefa ƙuri'a na Republican a za ~ en tsakiyar wa'adi.
Muna da makonni biyar kafin wani babban zabe a rayuwarmu.
Ba na gudu, amma a zahiri ina zuwa, in ji shi.
"Saboda haka nake tafiya ko'ina ina fafatawa don manyan 'yan takararmu".
Trump ya yi jayayya cewa 'yan Democrat suna yin "tsayayya da toshewa".
Ana sa ran za a fara zaben farko na majalisar dattijai kan nadin Kavanaugh a ranar Juma'a, a cewar wani mai taimakawa shugabannin jam'iyyar Republican.
Mutane da dama sun mutu a girgizar kasa da tsunami a Indonesia, inda adadin wadanda suka mutu ke karuwa
Akalla mutane 384 sun mutu, kuma da yawa sun shiga cikin manyan raƙuman ruwa da ke faɗuwa a bakin rairayin bakin teku, sakamakon mummunar girgizar ƙasa da tsunami da ta addabi tsibirin Sulawesi na Indonesia, in ji hukumomi a ranar Asabar.
Daruruwan mutane sun taru a ranar Juma'a don bikin bikin bakin teku a garin Palu lokacin da raƙuman ruwa masu tsawon mita shida suka buga bakin teku da yamma, suna jan mutane da yawa zuwa mutuwa da lalata duk abin da suka samu a hanyarsu.
Tsunami ya biyo bayan girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin 7.5.
Lokacin da barazanar tsunami ta zo jiya, mutane suna ci gaba da ayyukansu a bakin rairayin bakin teku kuma ba su gudu ba nan da nan. Saboda haka sun zama waɗanda aka kashe, in ji Sutopo Purwo Nugroho, mai magana da yawun hukumar rage bala'i BNPB a wata sanarwa a Jakarta.
 Tsunami din bai zo shi kadai ba, ya kwashe motoci, bishiyoyi, gidaje, ya rusa duk abin da ke ƙasa, in ji Nugroho, yana mai cewa tsunami ya yi tafiya a cikin teku mai sauri da sauri a kilomita 800 a kowace awa kafin ya buga gabar teku.
Ya ce wasu mutane sun tsere daga tsunami ta hanyar hawa kan bishiyoyi kuma sun tsira.
Kimanin mutane 16,700 ne aka kwashe zuwa cibiyoyi 24 a Palu.
Hotunan sama da hukumar kula da bala'i ta fitar da su da ke nuna yawan shaguna da gine-gine da suka lalace, gadaje da suka rushe da kuma masallaci da ke kewaye da ruwa.
An ci gaba da girgizar ƙasa a wannan garin da ke bakin teku a ranar Asabar.
An ji girgizar ƙasa a yankin da ke da mazauna miliyan 2.4.
Hukumar tantancewa da amfani da fasaha ta Indonesia (BPPT) ta ce a cikin wata sanarwa cewa makamashin da girgizar kasa mai tsanani ta saki a ranar Juma'a ya ninka na bam din atomic da aka jefa a Hiroshima a yakin duniya na biyu.
A cewar hukumar, yanayin yanayin garin, wanda ke ƙarshen doguwar gaɓar teku, na iya ƙara girman tsunami sosai.
Nugroho ya bayyana lalacewar a matsayin "mai yawa" kuma ya ce dubban gidaje, asibitoci, cibiyoyin kasuwanci da otal-otal sun rushe.
Ya ce an gano gawarwakin wasu daga cikin wadanda suka mutu a cikin rushewar gine-ginen da suka rushe, ya kara da cewa mutane 540 sun ji rauni kuma 29 sun bata.
A cewar Nugroho, mutuwar mutane da lalacewar na iya ƙaruwa a gabar teku kimanin kilomita 300 arewacin Palu, wani yanki da ake kira Donggala, mafi kusa da cibiyar girgizar ƙasar.
Sadarwa  ta kasance cikakkiyar gurgunta kuma saboda haka babu wani bayani da ya zo  daga Donggala, in ji Nugroho.
Akwai mutane sama da 300,000 da ke zaune a can, in ji kungiyar agaji ta Red Cross a wata sanarwa, ta kara da cewa ma'aikatanta da masu sa kai suna kan hanyarsu zuwa yankunan da abin ya shafa.
Wannan bala'i ne, wanda rashin alheri zai iya ƙare da muni sosai, in ji shi.
Hukumar ta sha suka sosai a ranar Asabar saboda rashin bayar da rahoton zuwan tsunami a Palu, duk da cewa jami'ai sun ce guguwar ta zo ne a lokacin da aka bayar da gargadin.
A wani bidiyo da wani mai son wasan ya wallafa a shafukan sada zumunta, ana iya jin wani mutum a saman wani gini yana ihu yana gargadi mutane a kan tituna game da guguwar tsunami mai zuwa.
A cikin 'yan mintoci kaɗan, ruwa ya soma zubowa a bakin tekun kuma ya halaka gine-gine da kuma motoci.
Kamfanin dillancin labarai na Reuters bai iya tabbatar da gaskiyar rikodin ba.
Girgizar kasa da tsunami sun haifar da katsewar wutar lantarki wanda ya katse sadarwa a kusa da Palu, yana wahalar da hukumomi wajen daidaita ayyukan ceto.
Duk da cewa sojoji sun fara aika da kayan agaji a cikin jiragen sama daga Jakarta da sauran biranen, jami'an sun ce mutanen da aka kwashe suna ci gaba da bukatar abinci da sauran kayan abinci.
Filin jirgin saman birnin ya sake buɗewa don ayyukan agaji ne kawai kuma zai kasance a rufe har zuwa Oktoba.
Shugaban kasar Joko Widodo ya shirya ziyartar cibiyoyin kwashe mutane a Palu ranar Lahadi.
Adadin mutanen da suka mutu a tsunami a Indonesia ya kai 800.
Yanayin yana da tsanani.
Duk da cewa ma'aikatan World Vision a Donggala sun isa garin Palu lafiya da lafiya, inda ma'aikata ke yin ruwa a cikin gidajen da aka sanya a cikin ofishin su, Doseba ya ce sun ga abubuwan da suka faru a kan hanyarsu.
"Sun ce sun ga gidaje da dama da aka lalata", in ji shi.
Wannan bala'i ne.
Duk da cewa kungiyoyin agaji sun yi bakin cikin fara aikin agaji, wasu mutane sun koka cewa ana hana ma'aikatan agaji tafiya zuwa Palu.
A cewar dokokin Indonesia, karbar kudade, kayayyaki da kuma ma'aikatan kasashen waje za su iya fara gudana ne kawai idan an ayyana wurin da bala'in ya auku a matsayin yankin bala'i na kasa.
Wannan bai faru ba tukuna.
Har yanzu bala'i ne a matakin lardin, in ji Aulia Arriani, mai magana da yawun kungiyar agaji ta Indonesiya.
Da zarar gwamnati ta ce "To, bala'i ne na kasa", za mu iya fara neman taimakon kasa da kasa, amma har yanzu ba a bayyana matakin ba.
Yayin da dare na biyu ya yi zafi a Palu bayan girgizar kasa da tsunami da ta faru a ranar Juma'a, abokai da dangin mutanen da suka bace suna fatan cewa mu'ujiza ta faru kuma ƙaunatattun su sun tsere wa mummunan labarin bala'in.
A ranar Asabar, an ceci wani yaro da ya makale a cikin wani bututun ruwa.
A ranar Lahadi, jami'an ceto sun ceto wata mata da aka binne a ƙarƙashin dutsen na kwana biyu tare da jikin mahaifiyarta a gefensa.
Gendon Subandono, kocin tawagar 'yan wasan kasar Indonesia, ya horar da biyu daga cikin 'yan wasan da suka bace a gasar wasannin Asiya, wadda ta kammala a farkon wannan watan a Indonesia.
Bayan Mr. Mandagi, wasu daga cikin mutanen da aka kama a otal din Roa Roa sun hada da dalibansa.
A matsayina na babban jami'in jirgin sama, ina da nawa nauyin motsin rai, in ji shi.
Mista Gendon ya bayyana cewa, a cikin sa'o'i bayan da labarin faduwar otal din Roa Roa ya bazu a tsakanin al'ummar masu tsalle-tsalle, ya aika da sakonnin WhatsApp ga masu fafatawa a Palu da ke halartar bikin rairayin bakin teku.
Duk da haka, saƙonnin sun bayyana tare da alamar tabbatarwa mai launin toka maimakon alamar biyu na blue.
Ya kara da cewa, "Ina ganin hakan na nufin ba a karɓi sakonnin ba".
Wasu 'yan fashi sun sace $ 26,750 yayin da suke cika wata asusu a Newport on the Levee
A ranar Juma'ar da ta gabata, 'yan fashi sun sace dala 26,750 daga wani ma'aikacin Brink's wanda ke cika wani akwatin ajiya a Newport on the Levee, a cewar sanarwar manema labarai da ofishin 'yan sanda na Newport ya fitar.
Jami'in Dennis McCarthy ya bayyana a cikin sanarwar cewa direban motar yana zubar da kuɗin ATM a cikin wurin shakatawa kuma yana shirya shi don ya ba da ƙarin kuɗi.
Yayin da yake aikinsa, wani mutum es ya zo yana gudu daga baya na ma'aikacin Brink's kuma ya sace masa jaka na kudi da aka yi niyya don rarraba.
