Taron Trump a West Virginia, tashar YouTube
Shugaba Donald Trump ya fara wani gagarumin gangamin yakin neman zabe a daren yau a birnin Wheeling na jihar West Virginia.
Wannan shi ne na farko daga cikin tarurruka biyar da Trump ya shirya yi a mako mai zuwa, wanda ya hada da ziyarar wurare masu kyau kamar Tennessee da Mississippi.
Yayin da ake jiran zaben tabbatar da wanda zai tsaya a kotun kolin, Trump na son samun goyon baya a zaben da za a yi a tsakiyar wa'adinsa, saboda 'yan Republican na fuskantar barazanar rasa iko a majalisar dokoki lokacin da aka kada kuri'un a watan Nuwamba.
A wane lokaci ne taron Trump a West Virginia a daren yau kuma ta yaya za a iya kallon sa ta yanar gizo?
An shirya taron Trump a Wheeling, West Virginia, da karfe 7 na yammacin yau Asabar, 29 ga Satumba, 2018.
Za a iya kallon taron Trump a West Virginia a kan layi a mahaɗin da aka ƙayyade a ƙasa, ta hanyar watsa shirye-shiryen bidiyo ta YouTube.
Ana sa ran Trump zai shiga sauraron karar da aka fara a wannan makon game da wanda aka zaba a Kotun Koli, Brett Kavanaugh, wanda ya kasance mai matukar damuwa saboda zargin cin zarafin da yake fuskanta, yayin da aka ci gaba da jiran kuri'ar tabbatar da Majalisar Dattawa har zuwa mako guda kuma FBI na binciken lamarin.
Amma babban manufar taron shi ne taimaka wa 'yan Republican da ke neman takara a zaben da za a yi a watan Nuwamba su samu ci gaba.
Saboda haka, taron yakin neman zaben shugaban kasa Trump guda biyar da aka shirya a mako mai zuwa suna nufin karfafa masu sa kai da masu goyon baya, yayin da 'yan Republican ke kokarin karewa da fadada rinjaye da suke da su a majalisar dattijai da majalisar wakilai, a cewar Reuters.
"Sarrafa majalisar dokoki yana da mahimmanci ga ajandar shugaban da zai yi tafiya zuwa jihohi da yawa kamar yadda zai iya, yayin da muke fuskantar lokacin kamfen mai cike da aiki", in ji wani kakakin Trump wanda ya ƙi bayyana sunansa, a cewar Reuters.
Taron na yau da dare, wanda aka shirya a Wesbanco Arena, Wheeling, na iya tara masu goyon baya daga Ohio da Pennsylvania, kuma su jawo hankalin kafofin watsa labarai na Pittsburgh, a cewar West Virginia Metro News.
A ranar Asabar ne karo na biyu da Trump ya ziyarci jihar West Virginia, jihar da ya lashe da kashi 40 cikin dari a shekarar 2016.
Trump yana kokarin taimaka wa Patrick Morrisey, dan takarar majalisar dattijai na Republican na West Virginia, wanda ke samun sakamako mara kyau a cikin binciken.
"Ba alama ce mai kyau ba ga Morrisey cewa shugaban ya zo ya ba shi ci gaba a cikin binciken", in ji Simon Haeder, masanin siyasa a Jami'ar West Virginia, a cewar Reuters.
Ryder Cup 2018: Ƙungiyar Amurka ta nuna burinta na ci gaba da kasancewa da bege a gaban wasannin da za a yi a ranar Lahadi
Bayan zaman uku da ba daidai ba, wasannin wasannin ranar Asabar da yamma sun kasance abin da wannan gasar Ryder Cup ta buƙaci.
Tsarin motsa jiki na motsa jiki wani ra'ayi ne na wasanni wanda aka ƙirƙira, wanda 'yan wasan suka gaskata da gaske, musamman a wasanni kamar wannan.
To, a wane gefe ne wannan kyakkyawan motsi yake yanzu?
"Suna da maki shida a gaba kuma yanzu suna da hudu, don haka ina tsammanin muna cikin wani ɗan gajeren lokaci mai kyau", in ji Jordan Spieth yayin da yake barin ƙarshen rana.
A bayyane yake, Turai tana da ci gaba, maki hudu a gaba, tare da karin maki 12.
Amurkawa, kamar yadda Spieth ya ce, suna jin cewa iska tana busawa a cikin ni'imarsu kuma suna da dalilai da yawa don yin farin ciki, galibi saboda yanayin Spieth da Justin Thomas, waɗanda suka yi wasa tare duk rana kuma duka suna da maki uku daga huɗu.
Spieth ya kasance mai kisa daga tee zuwa green kuma yana kafa misali.
Muryar murya ta murna ta tashi yayin da yake ci gaba da zagaye kuma ya buga wani muhimmin putt don daidaita wasan na huɗu, lokacin da shi da Thomas suka kasance biyu bayan ramuka biyu.
Ya yi bikin nasarar da suka samu a rami na 15 tare da irin wannan ihu, irin wannan wanda ya nuna cewa ya yi imanin cewa kungiyar Amurka ba ta fita daga gasar ba.
Spieth ya ce, "Ya kamata ka yi iya ƙoƙarinka kuma ka damu da jam'iyyarka".
Wannan shi ne abin da ya rage wa 'yan wasan yanzu.
18 ramuka don yin sawun.
'Yan wasa kawai da suka fi Spieth da Thomas maki a cikin kwanaki biyu da suka gabata sune Francesco Molinari da Tommy Fleetwood, wanda ba a iya jayayya da shi ba a gasar cin kofin Ryder.
Wasu ma'aurata 'yan Turai suna da kyau sosai, kuma ba sa yin kuskure.
Moliwood su ne kawai ma'aurata da ba su yi bogey a ranar Asabar da yamma ba, kuma sun kuma guje wa bogey a ranar Asabar da safe da Jumma'a da yamma, kuma na karshe tara a ranar Jumma'a da safe.
Saboda wannan sakamakon da kuma yadda makamashinsa ya bayyana yana gudana zuwa da kuma daga cikin masu sauraro, an tabbatar da cewa su ne 'yan wasan da za su buga ranar Lahadi, kuma babu wani ɗan wasa da ya fi Fleetwood ko Molinari shahara don rufe yiwuwar nasarar Turai yayin da rana ta faɗi a kan Le Golf National.
Zai fi kyau duka biyu a lokaci guda a cikin ramuka daban-daban.
Duk da haka, magana game da ɗaukakar Turai ta zama kamar ba ta da kyau.
Bubba Watson da Webb Simpson sun gama da Sergio Garcia, jarumin wasan kwallon kafa na safe, wanda ya haɗu da Alex Noren.
Wani bogey da biyu a cikin ramuka tara na farko sun jefa Spaniard da Swede a cikin rami wanda ba su da wata hanyar fita.
Amma a ranar Lahadi, babu wanda zai taimake ka ka fita daga cikin rami.
Wasanni na Fourball da kuma wasan ƙwallon ƙafa suna da ban sha'awa sosai don kallon yadda kayan aiki ke hulɗa, shawarwarin da suke bayarwa da waɗanda ba su bayar ba, da kuma yadda dabarun da za su iya canzawa ba zato ba tsammani.
Ya zuwa yanzu, Turai ta yi wasa mafi kyau a matsayin ƙungiya kuma za ta fuskanci rana ta ƙarshe tare da babbar nasara, amma wannan taron wasan kwaikwayo ya nuna cewa ƙungiyar Amurka tana da dalili don yin gwagwarmaya wanda wasu, musamman a Amurka, sun yi tambaya.
Turai ta kai wasan karshe na Ryder Cup da ci 10-6
Turai za ta fuskanci ranar karshe ta gasar cin kofin Ryder tare da amfani mai kyau bayan kammala wasan kwallon kafa da kuma wasan kwaikwayo a ranar Asabar tare da nasara 10 zuwa 6 akan Amurka.
Ma'aurata masu ban sha'awa Tommy Fleetwood da Francesco Molinari sun yi ƙoƙari sosai don samun nasara biyu akan Tiger Woods a cikin wahala kuma sun bar rikodin su, har zuwa yanzu, a cikin maki huɗu a Le Golf National.
Ƙungiyar Turai, wadda Thomas Bjorn ya jagoranci, wanda ke son ci gaba da cin nasarar da ya rasa shekaru biyu da suka gabata a Hazeltine, ya mamaye wani rukunin Amurka wanda ba shi da kyau a wasan safiya kuma ya sa jerin su 3-1.
Amurka ta nuna juriya ga masu tsere kuma ta ci wasanni biyu, amma ba ta iya rage bambance-bambance ba.
Kungiyar Jim Furyk ta bukaci samun maki takwas a wasanni 12 na ranar Lahadi don riƙe kyautar.
Fleetwood shine dan wasan Turai na farko da ya zira kwallaye hudu a jere, yayin da shi da Molinari, wanda aka fi sani da suna Molliwood bayan karshen mako mai ban sha'awa, sune kawai ma'aurata biyu da suka ci kwallaye hudu a cikin wasanninsu hudu a tarihin Ryder Cup.
Bayan sun doke Woods da Patrick Reed a cikin hudu, sun yi wasan kwaikwayo mai ban mamaki don doke Woods da kuma dan wasan Amurka Bryson Dechambeau don 5 & 4 har ma da mahimmanci.
Woods, wanda ya yi fama da rashin lafiya a wasanni biyu a ranar Asabar, ya nuna wasu abubuwa masu ban mamaki, amma ya rasa 19 daga cikin wasanni 29 a cikin wasan hudu da kuma wasanni bakwai.
Justin Rose, wanda bai shiga cikin wasannin safiya ba, ya sake yin hulɗa da Henrik Stenson a cikin wasan ƙwallon ƙafa kuma ya faɗi 2 zuwa 1 da Dustin Johnson da Brooks Koepka, waɗanda aka lasafta su a matsayin na farko da na uku a duniya, bi da bi.
Amma, Turai ba ta da komai a rana mai kyau da iska a kudu maso yammacin Paris.
Jordan Spieth, zakaran gasar sau uku, da Justin Thomas sun kafa misali ga Amurkawa a ranar Asabar ta hanyar samun maki biyu.
Sun sami nasara mai ƙarfi ta 2 zuwa 1 akan Mutanen Espanya Jon Rahm da Ian Poulter a cikin wasan kwallon kafa kuma daga baya suka sake cin Poulter da Rory McIlroy da 4 zuwa 3 a cikin wasan kwallon kafa, bayan sun rasa ramuka biyu na farko.
Sau biyu kawai a tarihin gasar Ryder Cup wata kungiya ta sake samun bambanci na maki hudu a wasannin mutum, duk da cewa ƙungiyar Furyk, mai kare taken, kawai tana buƙatar daidaitawa don kiyaye shi.
Duk da haka, bayan kasancewa na biyu mafi kyau a cikin kwanaki biyu, yana da alama cewa wani hari na mako mai zuwa yana waje da shi.
Koriya ta Arewa ta ce ba za ta yi watsi da makamai ba  ba za ta taba yin hakan ba  idan ba a nuna alamar amincewa ba
Ministan harkokin wajen Koriya ta Arewa ya sanar da Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a ranar Asabar cewa takunkumin da ake ci gaba da sanyawa na kara tsananta shakkar Amurka kuma a irin wannan yanayi, kasar ba za ta kawar da makaman nukiliyarta ba.
Ri Yong Ho ya shaida wa babban taron shekara-shekara na kungiyar ta duniya cewa Koriya ta Arewa ta dauki "manyan matakai na alheri" a cikin shekarar da ta gabata, kamar dakatar da gwajin makaman nukiliya da makamai masu linzami, rushe cibiyar gwajin nukiliya da kuma yin alkawarin rashin yaduwar makaman nukiliya da fasaha.
Duk da haka, ba mu lura da wani martani da ya dace da Amurka ba, in ji shi.
Ba tare da amincewa da Amurka ba, ba za a amince da tsaron kasa ba, kuma a karkashin wadannan yanayi, ba za mu fara kwance makamai ba a wata hanya.
Duk da yake Ri ya yi tir da sanannun korafin Koriya ta Arewa game da juriyar Washington game da tsarin 'yanke nukiliya  a matakai  wanda Koriya ta Arewa za ta ba da lada yayin da ta ɗauki matakai a hankali, maganganun sa sun zama masu mahimmanci saboda bai ƙi cikakken kawar da nukiliya ba, kamar yadda Pyongyang ta yi a baya.
Ri ya yi nuni da sanarwar hadin gwiwa da Kim Jong Un da Donald Trump suka yi a taron koli na farko tsakanin shugaban Amurka da shugaban Koriya ta Arewa a Singapore a ranar 12 ga Yuni, inda Kim ya yi alkawarin yin aiki kan denuclearization na yankin Koriya, yayin da Trump ya yi alkawarin tabbatar da tsaron Koriya ta Arewa.
Koriya ta Arewa ta yi ƙoƙarin kawo ƙarshen Yaƙin Koriya na 1950-53, amma Amurka ta sanar da cewa Pyongyang dole ne ta kawar da makaman nukiliyarta da farko.
Washington ta kuma yi tsayayya da kiran da ake yi na sassauta tsauraran takunkumin da aka kakaba wa Koriya ta Arewa.
Amurka ta dage kan cewa dole ne a fara yin yunkurin kawar da makaman nukiliya da farko kuma ta kara matsin lamba ta hanyar sanya takunkumi don cimma burinta ta hanyar tilastawa, ban da adawa da bayyanar karshen yakin, Ri ya ce.
Ganin cewa takunkumi zai sa mu durƙusa shine mafarkin mutanen da basu san komai game da mu ba.
Amma matsalar ita ce, takunkumi na ci gaba da kara tsananta mana rashin amincewa.
Ri bai ambaci shirin gudanar da taron koli na biyu tsakanin Kim da Trump ba wanda shugaban Amurka ya nuna a Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a farkon makon.
Maimakon haka, ministan ya nuna tarurruka uku tsakanin Kim da shugaban Koriya ta Kudu Moon Jae-in a cikin watanni biyar da suka gabata kuma ya kara da cewa: Idan bangaren da ke da hannu kan batun batun haramta nukiliya ya kasance Koriya ta Kudu maimakon Amurka, haramta nukiliya a yankin Koriya ba zai kai ga wannan halin da ake ciki ba.
Duk da haka, sautin jawabin Ri ya sha bamban da na shekarar da ta gabata, lokacin da ya bayyana a Majalisar Dinkin Duniya cewa harin da aka kai wa Amurka da makaman nukiliya na Koriya ta Arewa ba zai yiwu ba bayan Shugaba Trump ya kira Kim "Rocket Man" a cikin aikin kashe kansa.
A wannan shekara a Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, Trump, wanda a bara ya yi barazanar hallaka  Koriya ta Arewa, ya yaba wa Kim saboda ƙarfin hali don ɗaukar matakan kwantar da hankali, amma ya ce har yanzu akwai sauran aiki da yawa da za a yi kuma dole ne a ci gaba da takunkumi har sai Koriya ta Arewa ta kawar da makaman nukiliya.
A ranar Laraba da ta gabata, Trump ya ce babu wani wa'adi da zai sa a yi hakan kuma "ba damuwa ko zai dauki shekaru biyu ko uku ko watanni biyar".
China da Rasha sun ce Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta amince da matakin da Pyongyang ta dauka.
Duk da haka, Sakataren Harkokin Wajen Amurka, Mike Pompeo, ya bayyana a ranar Alhamis a Majalisar Dinkin Duniya cewa: Amfani da takunkumin Majalisar Dinkin Duniya dole ne ya ci gaba da ƙarfi kuma ba tare da wani banda ba har sai mun tabbatar da cikakken kuma tabbataccen lalata nukiliya.
Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta amince da takunkumi kan Koriya ta Arewa tun shekara ta 2006 a wani mataki na yanke kudaden da take baiwa Pyongyang don shirye-shiryen makaman nukiliya da na makaman nukiliya.
Pompeo ya gana da Ri a waje da Babban Taron Majalisar Dinkin Duniya sannan ya sanar da cewa zai sake ziyartar Pyongyang a watan gobe don shirya taron kolin na biyu.
Pompeo ya ziyarci Koriya ta Arewa sau uku a wannan shekarar, amma tafiyarsa ta ƙarshe ba ta tafi da kyau ba.
Ya bar Pyongyang a watan Yuli yana cewa an sami ci gaba, amma bayan 'yan sa'o'i kaɗan Koriya ta Arewa ta zarge shi da yin "buƙatun' yan daba".
A wani taron da Moon ya yi a wannan watan, Koriya ta Arewa ta yi alkawarin rushe cibiyar kera makamai masu linzami da kuma cibiyar nukiliya idan Amurka ta dauki "matakai daidai".
Ya ce Kim ya sanar da shi cewa matakan da suka dace da yake nema sune matakan tsaro da Trump ya yi alkawari a Singapore, ban da ayyukan daidaita dangantaka da Washington.
Daliban Harvard suna koyar da darasi game da yadda za a huta
A wannan shekarar, wani sabon darasi a Jami'ar Harvard ya ba dalibansa damar yin karin barci, a kokarin da suke yi na magance al'adar da ke karuwa ta yin nazari duk dare, ta hanyar shan maganin kafeyin.
Wani masanin kimiyya ya lura cewa ɗaliban da ke jami'a mafi girma a duniya suna yawan rasa ainihin abubuwan da za su yi don su kula da kansu.
Charles Czeisler, Farfesa a Magungunan Barci a Makarantar Likitancin Harvard kuma kwararre a Asibitin Brigham da Mata, ya tsara karatun, wanda ya yi imanin cewa shi ne na farko a cikin irin wannan a Amurka.
An yi wahayi zuwa gare shi don ƙirƙirar wannan hanya bayan ya ba da jawabi game da tasirin rashin barci akan ilmantarwa.
A ƙarshen jawabin, wata yarinya ta zo wurina kuma ta ce, "Me ya sa kuke gaya mini wannan a yanzu, a shekarata ta ƙarshe?"
Ta ce ba wanda ya taɓa gaya mata muhimmancin barci, abin da ya ba ni mamaki", in ji jaridar The Telegraph.
A cikin wannan darasin, wanda aka fara amfani da shi a wannan shekara, an bayyana wa ɗalibai ainihin abubuwan da ke cikin yadda kyawawan halaye na barci ke inganta aikin ilimi da wasanni, ban da jin daɗin rayuwa.
Paul Barreira, Farfesa a fannin ilimin halayyar dan adam a Harvard Medical School kuma babban darektan jami'ar kiwon lafiya, ya ce jami'ar ta yanke shawarar gabatar da karatun ne bayan da ta gano cewa wasu dalibai suna fama da matsalar rashin bacci a cikin mako.
Wannan darasi na tsawon awa ɗaya ya ƙunshi ayyuka masu ma'amala.
A wani sashe, akwai hoton ɗakin kwana inda ɗalibai za su danna kan kofunan kofi, labule, bamboo da littattafai don samun bayani game da tasirin maganin kafeyin da haske, yadda rashin barci ke shafar wasan motsa jiki, da kuma muhimmancin yin barci.
A wani sashe kuma, an koya wa masu halartar taron yadda rashin barci na dogon lokaci zai iya sa su kamu da ciwon zuciya, bugun jini, baƙin ciki da kuma ciwon daji.
Bayan haka, taswirar harabar da ke da gumakan hulɗa suna ƙarfafa mahalarta suyi tunani game da hanyarsu ta yau da kullun.
Mun san cewa halin ɗaliban ba zai canja nan da nan ba.
Amma mun gaskata cewa suna da hakkin su san, kamar yadda mutum yake da hakkin sanin lafiyar shan taba sigari", in ji Farfesa Czeisler.
Ya ce, har yanzu akwai al'adar yin alfahari da yin barci duk dare, ya kuma ce, fasahar zamani da kuma matsin lamba da ɗalibai ke fuskanta suna sa rashin barci ya zama matsala mai girma.
Tabbatar da samun isasshen barci mai kyau ya kamata ya zama makamin sirri na ɗalibai don magance damuwa, gajiya da damuwa, in ji shi, har ma don kauce wa samun nauyi, saboda rashin bacci yana sanya kwakwalwa cikin yanayin barci kuma yana sa ɗalibai su ci gaba da jin yunwa.
Raymond So, ɗan shekara 19 daga California wanda ke nazarin ilmin sunadarai da ilimin kimiyyar lissafi, ya taimaka wa Farfesa Czeisler wajen tsara darasin, bayan ya halarci ɗayan karatunsa a shekarar ƙarshe a shekararsa ta farko a Harvard.
Raymond ya yi sharhi cewa wannan darasi ya buɗe idanunsa kuma ya sa ya yi wahayi zuwa ga inganta darasin a ko'ina cikin harabar.
Mataki na gaba, kamar yadda yake fata, shine a tambayi daliban digiri na biyu suyi irin wannan shirin na nazarin kafin su shiga cikin makarantar da ke gasa.
Farfesa Czeisler ya ba da shawarar cewa ɗalibai su yi la'akari da saita ƙararrawa lokacin da suke barci da lokacin da suka farka, kuma su san illolin tasirin haske mai haske na lantarki da fitilun LED, wanda zai iya canza jituwa na circadian rhythm kuma ya haifar da matsalolin bacci.
Livingston 1-0 Rangers: Goal na Menga ya kawo karshen mutanen Gerrard
Golan Dolly Menga ya yanke wa tawagar Steven Gerrard hukuncin rashin nasara 1-0 a gidan Livingston wanda ya zama wani abin takaici a waje.
Gasar ta Ibrox ta nemi ta lashe gasar a gida tun daga 4-1 da suka yi a St Johnstone a watan Fabrairu, amma kungiyar Gary Holt ta sha kashi na biyu a hannun Gerrard a wasanni 18 a matsayin kociyar ta bar ta a kan hanya, maki 8 daga Hearts, shugabannin da ba za a iya dakatar da su ba a Ladbrokes Premiership.
Menga ya zira kwallo minti bakwai kafin rabin wasa, kuma bai taɓa zama kamar Rangers ba, ba tare da wahayi ba, yana gab da daidaita ci.
Yayin da Rangers yanzu suka sauka a matsayi na shida, Livingston ya hau zuwa matsayi na uku, a bayan Hibernian ta hanyar raga.
Kuma Rangers na iya fuskantar ƙarin wahala daga baya, yayin da alkalin wasa Calum Spence ya buƙaci kulawa ta likita saboda raunin da ya faru a kansa wanda wani abu ya bayyana daga filin wasa.
Gerrard ya yi canje-canje takwas game da ƙungiyar da ta kori Ayr a wasan kusa da na ƙarshe na Betfred Cup.
Holt, a gefe guda, ya fito da wannan wasan farko guda 11 da ya zira kwallo a karawar da suka yi da Hearts a makon da ya gabata.
Ko da yake Rangers sun mallaki mallakar, Livingston ya haifar da mafi haɗari lokacin da suke da ball.
A zahiri, ya kamata su ci kwallo a cikin mintuna biyu na wasan, lokacin da sa hannun farko na Menga ya bar Scot Pittman shi kaɗai a gaban Allan McGregor, amma mai tsaron tsakiya ya taka hanya kuma ya rasa babbar damar.
Wani mummunan kuskure daga Keaghan Jacobs ya buga wa kyaftin Craig Halkett, amma abokin aikinsa Alan Lithgow ya yi kawai a cikin baya.
Rangers sun yi nasara a kan iko, amma sun yi kamar suna da bege fiye da bangaskiya a wasan su a ƙarshen na uku.
Alfredo Morelos ya yi imanin cewa ya kamata ya sami hukuncin kisa a alamar minti goma sha biyar, saboda shi da Steven Lawless sun ci karo, amma alkalin wasa Steven Thomson ya yi watsi da da'awar ɗan Colombia.
Rangers sun yi amfani da harbi biyu ne kawai a raga a farkon rabin, amma mai tsaron gidan Ibrox, Liam Kelly, bai sami matsala ba tare da bugun Lassana Coulibaly da mai tsaron gida Ovie Ejaria.
Duk da yake aikin farko na Livi a minti na 34 na iya zama a kan tseren, babu wanda zai iya musun cewa sun cancanci hakan kawai saboda ƙoƙarin su.
Har ila yau, Rangers ba su iya magance aikin da Jacobs ya yi ba.
Scott Arfield bai amsa ba lokacin da Declan Gallagher ya ba da kwallon zuwa Scott Robinson, wanda ya kasance mai hankali don zaɓar Menga don ƙarshen kawai.
Gerrard ya yi aiki a lokacin hutu ta hanyar maye gurbin Coulibaly da Ryan Kent. Canjin ya yi tasiri kusan nan da nan, saboda ƙarshen ya ba da gudummawa ga Morelos, duk da cewa Kelly mai ban mamaki ya gudu zuwa toshewa.
Duk da haka, Livingstons sun ci gaba da jan hankalin baƙi suna wasa daidai yadda suke so, tare da Lithgow da Halkett suna yin doguwar tafiya, ɗaya bayan ɗaya.
Holt's band zai iya ba da jagorancin a cikin matakai na ƙarshe, amma McGregor ya tsaya tsayin daka don ya ƙi Jacobs kafin Lithgow ya yi tsalle daga kusurwa.
Har ila yau, mai maye gurbin Rangers Glenn Middleton ya nemi hukuncin kisa na karshe don jayayya da Jacobs, amma kuma Thomson ya yi ido.
Almanac: Mai kirkirar Geiger counter
Yanzu shafi na 30 ga Satumba, 1882 a cikin "Sunday Morning Almanac" shekaru 136 da suka gabata, ranar da aka haifi Johannes Wilhelm "Hans" Geiger a Jamus.
Geiger ya kirkiro wata hanya ta ganowa da auna aikin rediyo, wani abin kirkira wanda daga karshe ya haifar da na'urar da muka sani da Geiger counter.
Mai ƙididdigar Geiger, wanda ya kasance ginshiƙi na kimiyya tun daga wannan lokacin, ya zama ginshiƙin al'adun gargajiya, kamar fim ɗin 1950 "Bells of Coronado", wanda Roy Rogers da Dale Evans suka yi, masu fasahar lissafi masu ban mamaki:
Mutum: "Mene ne wannan a baya?"
Rogers: "Wannan Geiger counter ne, wanda ake amfani da shi wajen gano ma'adanai masu saurin rediyo, kamar uranium.
Idan ka sa kunne, za ka iya jin tasirin da ƙwayoyin halitta ke yi a kan ma'adanai".
Evans: "Lalle ne yana fashewa yanzu!"
"Hans" Geiger ya mutu a shekara ta 1945, kwanaki kadan bayan ya cika shekara 63.
Amma abin da ya samo asali da sunansa yana nan da rai.
