HIV/AIDS: Kasar Sin ta ba da rahoton karuwar sabbin mutane da kashi 14 cikin 100
Kasar Sin ta sanar da karuwar kashi 14 cikin dari na yawan mutanen da ke dauke da cutar kanjamau da kanjamau.
Akwai mutane sama da 820,000 da cutar ta shafa a kasar, a cewar jami'an lafiya.
A cikin kwata na biyu na 2018 kadai, an bayyana sabbin mutane 40,000.
Yawancin sababbin cututtuka na hanyar jima'i ne, ba kamar yadda ya faru a dā ba.
A al'adance, cutar HIV tana yaduwa cikin sauri a wasu yankuna na kasar Sin saboda ƙarin jini mai cutar.
Duk da haka, yawan mutanen da ke kamuwa da cutar HIV daga wannan hanyar ya ragu zuwa kusan babu, in ji jami'an kiwon lafiya na kasar Sin a wani taro a lardin Yunnan.
Duk da haka, a kowace shekara, adadin mutanen da ke da cutar kanjamau da kanjamau a China ya ƙaru da mutane 100,000.
Yaduwar cutar kanjamau ta hanyar jima'i babbar matsala ce ga al'ummar LGBT a China.
An dakatar da nuna luwadi a kasar Sin a shekarar 1997, amma nuna bambanci ga LGBT ya zama ruwan dare gama gari.
Idan aka yi la'akari da dabi'un da ke cikin kasar, binciken ya kiyasta cewa tsakanin kashi 70 zuwa 90 cikin dari na maza da ke da dangantaka da maza suna yin aure da mace.
Yawancin cututtuka suna yaduwa ne saboda rashin kiyayewa a lokacin jima'i.
Tun shekara ta 2003, gwamnatin kasar Sin ta yi alkawarin samar da maganin cutar HIV ga kowa a kasar a matsayin wani bangare na kokarin magance matsalar.
Maxine Waters ta musanta cewa wani ma'aikaci ya fallasa bayanan Sanatocin Jam'iyyar Republican kuma ta fallasa "ƙaryace-ƙaryace masu haɗari" da "ka'idodin makirci"
Wakilin Amurka Maxine Waters a ranar Asabar ta yi tir da zargin cewa wani ma'aikacinsa ya wallafa bayanan sirri na sanatocin Amurka uku na Republican a shafukan Wikipedia na 'yan majalisa.
Democrat din daga Los Angeles ta yi iƙirarin cewa masu sukar da shafukan yanar gizo masu tsattsauran ra'ayi ne suka gabatar da buƙatun.
"Maƙaryaci, ƙarya da ƙarin munanan ƙarya", Waters ya bayyana a cikin wata sanarwa a Twitter.
An ce bayanan da aka buga sun ƙunshi adiresoshin da lambobin waya na Sanata Lindsey Graham na Amurka, daga South Carolina, da Mike Lee da Orrin Hatch, duka daga Utah.
Bayanan sun bayyana a yanar gizo a ranar Alhamis kuma wani wanda ba a san shi ba ya buga shi a cikin Capitol yayin zaman kwamitin majalisar dattijai game da zargin cin zarafin dan takarar kotun koli Brett Kavanaugh.
Bayan da wasu sanatoci uku suka yi wa Kavanaugh tambayoyi, sai aka samu labarin.
Shafukan yanar gizo masu ra'ayin mazan jiya, kamar Gateway Pundit da RedState, sun ba da rahoton cewa adireshin IP ɗin da ke gano tushen bayanan yana da alaƙa da ofishin Waters kuma yana bayyana bayanan wani ma'aikacin Waters, babban birnin ya yi korafi.
"Wannan tuhumar da ba ta da tushe ba ƙarya ce kuma ƙarya ce", Waters ya ci gaba.
"Memba na wanda aka yi wa barazana da sunansa da bayanansa da kuma tsaronsa sakamakon wadannan rahotanni na karya da na zamba, ba shi da alhakin wannan bayanan da aka fitar.
Wannan tuhuma da ba ta da tushe ƙarya ce kuma ƙarya ce kawai".
Bayanin Waters ya haifar da suka kan layi da sauri, gami da tsohon sakataren yada labarai na fadar White House, Ari Fleischer.
"Wannan ƙin yarda da shi yana cike da fushi", in ji Fleischer.
"Wannan yana nuna cewa ba ku da halin zama dan majalisa.
Idan aka zargi wani da abin da bai yi ba, bai kamata ya yi fushi ba.
Kada ka nuna cewa kana da halin ƙiyayya.
Bai kamata ka yi shakkar dalilin da ya sa kake tuhumar wani ba.
Ya kamata ta kasance da kwanciyar hankali da kuma farin ciki".
Fleischer ya yi kama da kwatancin Waters da sukar da 'yan Democrat suka yi wa Alkali Kavanaugh, wanda masu sukar suka zarge shi da nuna fushi sosai a lokacin zaman ranar Alhamis.
Omar Navarro, dan takarar Republican wanda ke neman kawar da Waters a zaben tsakiyar shekara, ya kuma bayyana ra'ayinsa a Twitter.
"Ko da gaskiya ne", in ji shi.
A cikin jawabinsa, Waters ya ce ofishinsa ya gargadi hukumomi da jami'an tsaro game da waɗannan maganganun na yaudara.
"Za mu tabbatar da cewa an gano masu laifin", ya ci gaba, "kuma za a ɗora musu alhakin duk wani aiki da suka yi wanda ya cutar da kowane ma'aikacina".
