Wakilan jihohi 18 da gundumar sun gabatar da wata takarda ta amicus curiae a ranar Juma'a a Washington don tallafawa mai neman mafaka wanda ya kalubalanci manufofin, a cewar NBC News.
Ba a bayyana cikakken sunan karar da kungiyar kare hakkin bil adama ta Amurka ta shigar a watan Agusta ba game da dokar tarayya.
Ta ce ma'auratan ta "da 'ya'yan wani dan kungiyar masu ta'addanci" sun yi mata hari, amma jami'an Amurka sun hana ta neman mafaka a ranar 20 ga watan Yuli.
