Sabuwar manufar neman mafaka ta Amurka ta soke hukuncin da Hukumar Kula da Shige da Fice ta yanke a shekarar 2014, wanda ya baiwa 'yan ci-rani da ba su da takardun da za su iya tserewa daga tashin hankali na cikin gida damar neman mafaka.
Babban lauyan gundumar Columbia, Karl Racine, ya bayyana a ranar Juma'a cewa sabuwar manufar "ta yi watsi da shekarun da suka gabata na dokokin jihohi, tarayya da na duniya".
Dokokin tarayya sun bukaci a yanke hukunci kan aikace-aikacen neman mafaka bisa ga takamaiman gaskiya da yanayin da ake nema, kuma wannan haramcin ya sabawa wannan ƙa'idar, a cewar abokina curiae.
