Kamfanin ya kira shi "karfafawa mutum ta hanyar bayanai".
Manufar Inrupt, a cewar shugaban kamfanin John Bruce, shine kamfanin ya haɗa albarkatu masu dacewa, matakai da ƙwarewa don dandamali na Solid ya kasance ga kowa.
Kamfanin a halin yanzu ya ƙunshi Berners-Lee, Bruce, wani dandamali na tsaro da IBM ta saya, wasu masu haɓaka a cikin samfurin da aka ɗaura don aiki a kan aikin da kuma ƙungiyar masu aikin sa kai.
Daga wannan makon, masu haɓaka fasaha a duk faɗin duniya za su iya ƙirƙirar aikace-aikacen da aka rarraba ta amfani da kayan aikin da ke kan gidan yanar gizon Inrupt.
Berners-Lee ya ce babu wani a cikin tawagarsa da ke magana da "Facebook da Google game da ko za a kawo canji mai mahimmanci inda duk tsarin kasuwancin ke ɓoyewa gaba ɗaya cikin dare.
"Ba mu neman izinin su".
A cikin wani rubutu a ranar Asabar a Medium, Berners-Lee ya rubuta cewa Mashin Inrupt shine samar da wutar lantarki ta kasuwanci da kuma tsarin halittu don taimakawa kare mutuncin da ingancin sabon shafin yanar gizon da aka haɗa a cikin dandamali Solid.
A shekara ta 1994, Berners-Lee ya canza Intanet lokacin da ya kafa Ƙungiyar Yanar Gizo ta Duniya a Cibiyar Fasaha ta Massachusetts.
A cikin 'yan watannin da suka gabata, Berners-Lee ya kasance mai tasiri a cikin muhawara game da tsaka tsaki na yanar gizo.
Ko da lokacin ƙaddamar da Inrupt, Berners-Lee zai ci gaba da zama mai kafa da darektan World Wide Web Consortium, Gidauniyar Yanar gizo ta Duniya da Open Data Institute.
"Ina da kwarin gwiwa game da wannan sabon zamanin yanar gizo", in ji Berners-Lee.
