Laftanar Lt. Colonel kuma mai daraja Bernard Vann ya sami lambar yabo a ranar 29 ga Satumba, 1918 don kai hari a Bellenglise da Lehaucourt.
Duk da haka, an harbe shi da bindiga kwanaki huɗu bayan haka kuma bai taɓa sanin cewa ya sami babbar lambar girmamawa ta soja ta Burtaniya ba.
Jikansa biyu sun gano wani kabarin tunawa a ranar Asabar a Rushden, Northamptonshire.
Ɗaya daga cikin jikokinsa, Michael Vann, ya ce "mai alama ne mai ban mamaki" cewa an gabatar da kabarin daidai shekaru 100 bayan nasarar da kakansa ya samu.
A cewar The London Gazette, a ranar 29 ga Satumba, 1918, Lt. Col. Vann ya jagoranci rundunarsa ta hanyar Canal de Saint-Quentin "ta hanyar hazo mai yawa da kuma wuta mai tsanani daga bindigogi da bindigogi".
Daga baya ya gudu zuwa layin wuta kuma, tare da "ƙarfin ƙarfin hali" ya ci gaba da jere kafin ya jefa kansa a kan wani bindiga da hannu ɗaya kuma ya bar 'yan majalisa uku da mamaki.
An kashe Lieutenant Colonel ne daga wani dan jarida na Jamus a ranar 4 ga Oktoba, 1918, wata daya kafin yakin ya ƙare.
Michael Vann, mai shekara 72, ya ce ayyukan kakansa wani abu ne da ba zai taɓa iya daidaitawa ba, wanda ke sa ka ji tawali'u.
Shi da ɗan'uwansa, Dr. James Vann, sun kuma bar kambi bayan bikin, wanda Brentwood Imperial Youth Band ya gudanar.
Michael Vann ya ce yana jin girmamawa sosai da kasancewa cikin jerin sunayen kuma ya kara da cewa darajar jarumi na gaske ana nuna shi ta hanyar goyon bayan da zai samu daga mutane da yawa.
MMA magoya bayan da suka yi barci ba dare ba rana don kallon Bellator 206 sun ga Peppa Pig a maimakon
Ka yi tunanin cewa ka yi barci dukan dare kana kallon Bellator 206 kuma an hana ka kallon muhimmin abu.
San Jose ya ƙunshi gwagwarmaya 13, ciki har da shida daga cikin manyan katunan kuma ana kallon su kai tsaye a duk dare a Burtaniya akan Channel 5.
Da karfe 6:00, lokacin da Gegard Mousasi da Rory MacDonald ke shirin fuskantar juna, masu kallo a Burtaniya sun yi mamakin lokacin da aka canza jadawalin zuwa Peppa Pig.
Wasu sun yi fushi cewa sun yi barci har dare don su ga yadda ake faɗa.
Wani mai bin Twitter ya bayyana sauyawar zuwa zane-zane a matsayin "wani nau'i na zubar da jini".
"Dokar gwamnati ta ce a karfe 6:00 na safe wannan abun bai dace ba, don haka suka canza zuwa shirye-shiryen yara", in ji Dave Schwartz, mataimakin shugaban kasuwanci da sadarwa na Bellator, lokacin da aka tambaye shi game da watsa shirye-shiryen.
"Yana da kyau, ya yi kyau".
Shugaban kamfanin Bellator, Scott Coker, ya ce za su yi aiki a kan shirye-shiryen don haɗa masu kallon Burtaniya a nan gaba.
"Ina ganin lokacin da na yi tunani game da maimaitawa, ina tsammanin zai iya aiki", in ji Coker.
"Amma a can, sa'a shida na safe ne a ranar Lahadi, kuma ba za mu iya warware shi ba sai ranar Lahadi a lokacinmu, Litinin a lokacinku.
