Wannan mummunan yanayi ne".
Tom Daley ya ji ya zama ƙasa da ƙasa game da jima'i
Mai tsalle-tsalle na Olympics Tom Daley ya ce ya girma yana jin kasa da sauran mutane saboda jima'i, amma wannan ya ba shi dalili don cin nasara.
Dan wasan mai shekara 24 ya ce bai fahimci cewa ba kowa ba ne kamarsa har sai da ya shiga makarantar sakandare.
A shirin Desert Island Discs na Radio 4, wanda Lauren Laverne ya gabatar, ya ce yana magana ne game da 'yancin' yan luwadi don ba da bege ga wasu mutane.
Ya kuma ce zama uba bai sa ya yi farin ciki da nasarar da ya samu a gasar Olympics ba.
Kirsty Young, wadda ta daɗe tana gabatar da shirin, ta yi rashin lafiya na wasu watanni.
Daley, wanda ya bayyana a matsayin mai haɗari a farkon shirin Laverne, ya ce yana jin "ƙananan" wasu saboda "ba a yarda da shi ba a matsayin yara maza da mata".
Ya ce, "A yau, waɗannan ra'ayoyin na rashin cancanta da bambanci, abubuwa ne na gaske da suka ba ni iko da ƙarfin yin nasara".
Ya so ya tabbatar da cewa shi "wani abu ne", in ji shi, don kada ya ɓata wa kowa rai lokacin da ya gano jima'i.
Wanda ya lashe lambar tagulla ta Olympics sau biyu ya zama babban mai tallata LGBT kuma ya yi amfani da hotonsa a wasannin Commonwealth na wannan shekara a Ostiraliya don neman ƙarin ƙasashe su dakatar da luwadi.
Ta ce ta yi magana ne domin ta ji ta yi sa'a da za ta iya rayuwa a fili ba tare da wata matsala ba kuma tana son ta ba wasu mutane "bege".
Gwarzon duniya ya bayyana cewa ya ƙaunaci wani mutum, mai ba da fim na Amurka, Dustin Lance Black, wanda ya sadu da shi a 2013, "ya ba ni mamaki".
A shekarar da ta shige, Daley ta auri wani mutum mai shekaru 20 da haihuwa, wanda ya lashe kyautar Oscar. Amma ta ce bambancin shekaru bai taɓa zama matsala ba.
A cewarsa, idan ka shiga cikin matashi (ya shiga gasar Olympics ta farko lokacin da yake dan shekara 14 kuma mahaifinsa ya mutu daga ciwon daji shekaru uku daga baya), yana da wuya a sami wani a cikin shekarunsa wanda ya fuskanci irin wannan tashin hankali da kuma raguwa.
Ma'aurata sun zama iyaye a watan Yuni na ɗa wanda aka kira Robert Ray Black-Daley.
"Idan ka tambaye ni a bara, duk abin da nake bukata shi ne lashe zinare na Olympics", in ji ta.
"Akwai abubuwa da suka fi zinare na Olympics muhimmanci.
"Na lashe zinare na Olympics a matsayin Robbie".
Sunan ɗansa kamar mahaifinsa ne, Robert, wanda ya mutu a shekara ta 2011, yana da shekaru 40 saboda cutar kansa.
A cewar Daley, mahaifinsa bai yarda cewa ya mutu ba kuma daya daga cikin abubuwan da ya tambayi shi shine idan suna da tikiti zuwa London 2012 saboda yana so ya kasance a gaba.
"Ba zan iya gaya masa ba, 'Baba, ba za ka kasance a jere na farko ba,'" in ji ta.
"Yayin da na kama hannunsa, ya daina numfashi kuma ba sai lokacin da ya riga ya mutu ba, na yarda cewa ba a iya cin nasara ba", in ji ta.
A shekara mai zuwa, Daley ta yi gasa a gasar Olympics ta 2012 kuma ta lashe tagulla.
"Na san cewa wannan shi ne abin da na yi mafarkin rayuwata duka: tsalle a gaban taron jama'a a gida a wasannin Olympics. Babu wani abin da ya fi wannan jin", in ji ta.
Har ila yau, ta yi wahayi zuwa ga zabar waƙar farko (Proud na Heather Small), wanda ta ji a lokacin shirye-shiryen gasar Olympics kuma har yanzu yana sanya ta fata.
Desert Island Discs ana watsa shi ne a BBC Radio 4 a ranar Lahadi da karfe 11:15 BST.
