Dan wasan Amurka Phil Mickelson zai buga wasa na 47 a gasar Ryder Cup ranar Lahadi, amma dole ne ya canza yanayin jikinsa idan ba ya son ya zama abin takaici.
Mickelson, wanda zai shiga cikin taron na shekara biyu don karya rikodin karo na 12, ya gabatar da shi ne ta hanyar kyaftin Jim Furyk don yanayin fourballs da foursomes na ranar Asabar.
Maimakon zama a tsakiyar aikin, kamar yadda ya saba a Amurka, mai nasara na manyan wasanni biyar ya raba lokacinsa tsakanin yin wasan kwaikwayo da kuma aiki a kan wasan a filin wasa, yana fatan gyara abin da ke cutar da shi.
Bai taɓa yin direbobi kai tsaye ba, ko da a lokacin da ya fi dacewa da aikinsa, amma ɗan wasan mai shekaru 48 ba shi da zaɓi mai kyau don mawuyacin yanayin Le Golf National, inda dogon rough yakan hukunta ɓarna.
Kuma idan har ba ta da ƙarfin hali, Mickelson, a wasa na tara a ranar Lahadi, zai fafata da zakaran gasar Open ta Burtaniya, Francesco Molinari, wanda ya shiga rookie Tommy Fleetwood don cin nasara a wasanni hudu na wannan makon.
Idan Amurkawa, da suka rage maki hudu a wasan farko na wasanni 12, suka fara da karfi, wasan Mickelson zai iya zama mai mahimmanci.
