"Ya fahimci matsayinsa sosai a wannan ranar, ya buge ni a baya kuma ya kewaye ni da hannunsa yayin da yake gaya mani cewa zan kasance a shirye gobe", in ji Furyk.
"Yana da tabbaci sosai a kansa.
Shi ne mai gidan sarauta kuma ya kawo yawa ga wadannan teams baya da kuma wannan makon.
Wataƙila ban yi tunanin shi yana wasa biyu ba.
Na yi tunani game da shi, amma wannan shine yadda nake horarwa kuma wannan shine yadda muke tsammanin za mu ci gaba.
Yana son ya kasance a wurin, kamar kowa".
A ranar Lahadi, Mickelson zai doke rikodin Nick Faldo na mafi yawan wasannin Ryder Cup da aka buga.
Zai iya nufin ƙarshen wasan Ryder Cup wanda bai daidaita da rikodin mutum ba.
Mickelson ya samu nasara 18, shan kashi 20 da kuma ci 7 duk da cewa Furyk ya ce kasancewar sa ya kawo abubuwa da ba za a iya kamawa ba ga tawagar.
Yana da ban dariya, mai ba'a, mai ba'a, yana son yin ba'a da mutane kuma babban abokin aiki ne ga ƙungiyar, ya bayyana.
Ina tsammanin matasa 'yan wasa ma suna jin daɗin zama tare da shi a wannan makon, wanda ya kasance mai ban sha'awa don gani.
