Furyk ya san bangarorin biyu na tsabar kudin game da tashin hankali na ranar ƙarshe, saboda ya kasance cikin ƙungiyar da ta ci nasara a Brookline kafin ta ƙare ta rasa a Miracle of Medinah wanda ya ci Turai.
"Na tuna da dukan kalmomin daidai", in ji shi a lokacin da aka tambaye shi yadda Ben Crenshaw, kyaftin din 1999, ya karfafa 'yan wasansa kafin ranar karshe.
Muna da manyan wasanni 12 gobe, amma muna son mu fara da kyau, kamar yadda muka gani a Brookline da Madinah.
