Da yake jawabi ga Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, Ministan Harkokin Waje Walid al-Muallem ya yi kira ga 'yan gudun hijirar Syria da su koma gidajensu, duk da cewa an shafe shekaru takwas ana yaki a kasar.
