Girgizar ƙasa da tsunami a ƙasar Indonesia
Akalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu sakamakon wata girgizar kasa da tsunami da ta afkawa birnin Palu na kasar Indonesia a ranar Juma'a, a cewar hukumomi.
Saboda an yanke sadarwa, jami'an agaji ba su iya samun bayanai daga gundumar Donggala ba, wani yanki a arewacin Palu mafi kusa da cibiyar girgizar kasar mai karfin awo 7.5.
A Palu, an kwashe mutane sama da 16,000 bayan bala'in.
Ga wasu mahimman bayanai game da Palu da Donggala, a tsibirin Clebes:
Palu babban birnin lardin Cèlebes ta Tsakiya ne, wanda ke gefen wani kunkuntar bakin teku a yammacin tsibirin Cèlebes, tare da yawan mutane 379,800 a shekara ta 2017.
Birnin yana bikin cika shekaru 40 da kafuwarsa sa'ad da girgizar ƙasa da tsunami suka auku.
Donggala wani yanki ne wanda ya shimfiɗa tsawon kilomita 300 na gabar teku a arewa maso yammacin tsibirin Celebes.
Gundumar, yanki ne na gudanarwa ƙasa da lardi, yana da yawan jama'a kusan 299,200 a shekara ta 2017.
Kifi da noma sune ginshiƙan tattalin arzikin lardin Cèlebes ta Tsakiya, musamman a yankin Donggala na bakin teku.
Harkokin hakar ma'adinai na nickel ma yana da mahimmanci a lardin, amma an mayar da hankali ne, musamman, a Morowali, a bakin tekun a ƙarshen Cèlebes.
Palu da Donggala sun sha wahala tsunami da yawa a cikin shekaru 100 da suka gabata, a cewar hukumar kula da bala'i ta Indonesia.
A shekara ta 1938, tsunami ya kashe mutane fiye da 200 kuma ya halaka ɗaruruwan gidaje a Donggala.
A shekara ta 1996 kuma tsunami ya faru a yammacin Donggala wanda ya kashe mutane tara.
Indonesia tana cikin yankin da ake yawan girgizar ƙasa a cikin tekun Pacific.
An lissafa manyan girgizar ƙasa da tsunami na 'yan shekarun nan:
2004: A ranar 26 ga Disamba, wata babbar girgizar ƙasa a gabar yammacin lardin Aceh na Indonesia, a arewacin Sumatra, ta haifar da tsunami wanda ya shafi ƙasashe 14 kuma ya kashe mutane 226,000 a gabar tekun Indiya, fiye da rabi daga cikinsu a Aceh.
2005: An yi wata babbar girgizar ƙasa a yammacin Sumatra a ƙarshen Maris da farkon Afrilu.
Dubban mutane sun mutu a tsibirin Nias, a bakin tekun Sumatra.
2006: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin 6.8 ta afku a kudancin Java, tsibiri mafi yawan jama'a a Indonesia, kuma ta haifar da tsunami wanda ya lalata gabar kudu kuma ya kashe kusan mutane 700.
2009: Wata girgizar kasa mai karfin awo 7.6 ta afkawa wani yanki da ke kusa da birnin Padang, babban birnin lardin Sumatra ta Yamma.
Mutane fiye da 1,100 ne suka mutu.
2010: Wata girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 7.5 ta girgiza tsibirin Mentawai, a gabar tekun Sumatra, kuma ta haifar da tsunami mai tsayi har mita 10 wanda ya lalata ƙauyuka da yawa kuma ya kashe mutane 300.
2016: Wata girgizar kasa mai rauni ta shafi yankin Pidie Jaya a Aceh kuma ta haifar da lalacewa da firgici yayin da jama'a ke tuna bala'in girgizar kasa da tsunami na 2004.
A wannan lokacin, babu wata guguwar tsunami, amma mutane fiye da 100 sun mutu saboda gine-ginen da suka rushe.
2018: An yi wata babbar girgizar ƙasa a tsibirin Lombok na Indonesia wanda ya kashe mutane sama da 500, galibi a arewacin tsibirin.
Girgizar ta rushe dubban gine-gine kuma ta bar dubban masu yawon bude ido a makale na ɗan lokaci.
An kama babban dan Sarah Palin bisa zargin cin zarafin mata
Track Palin, babban dan tsohon gwamnan Alaska kuma dan takarar mataimakin shugaban kasa Sarah Palin, an kama shi da laifin cin zarafi.
An kama Palin, mai shekara 29, dan asalin Wasilla, Alaska, a kan zargin cin zarafin gida, tsoma baki a rahoton cin zarafin gida da kuma tsayayya da kama, a cewar rahoton da jami'an 'yan sanda na jihar Alaska suka fitar a ranar Asabar.
A cewar rahoton 'yan sanda, lokacin da wata abokiyarta ta yi ƙoƙarin kiran' yan sanda don bayar da rahoton zargin aikata laifuka, ta ba ta wayar.
Palin yana tsare a cibiyar tsare mutane ta Mat-Su inda aka tsare shi a kan bashin da ba a biya ba na dala 500, a cewar KTUU.
Ya bayyana a kotu a ranar Asabar, lokacin da ya bayyana "ba shi da laifi, tabbas" lokacin da aka tambaye shi yadda ya bayyana, a cewar wannan tashar.
Palin yana fuskantar laifuffuka uku na aji A, wanda ke nufin zai iya shiga kurkuku har zuwa shekara guda kuma ya biya tarar har zuwa $ 250,000.
An kuma tuhume ta da laifin Class B, wanda ake iya hukunta shi da kwana daya a kurkuku da kuma $ 2,000 a tara.
Wannan ba shine karo na farko da aka fara tuhumar Palin ba.
A watan Disamba na shekara ta 2017 an zarge shi da cin zarafin mahaifinsa, Todd Palin.
Mahaifiyarsa, Sarah Palin, ta kira 'yan sanda don sanar da zargin da ake yi.
Yanzu haka, kotun Alaska ta yanke hukunci a kan wannan shari'ar.
A watan Janairun 2016 an zarge shi da cin zarafin gida, tsoma baki tare da rahoton wani laifi na tashin hankali na gida da kuma mallakar makami a cikin maye dangane da lamarin.
Abokinsa ya shaida cewa ya buge shi a fuskarsa.
A shekara ta 2016, kungiyoyin tsoffin sojoji sun soki Sarah Palin saboda ta danganta halin ɗanta na tashin hankali da rikicewar damuwa ta bayan-tashin hankali wanda ya samo asali daga hidimarsa a Iraki.
