Masu gabatar da kara na tarayya sun nemi a yankewa wanda ake zargi da kai harin ta'addanci hukuncin kisa
Masu gabatar da kara a New York sun nemi a yankewa Sayfullo Saipov hukuncin kisa, wanda ake zargi da kai harin ta'addanci a New York wanda ya kashe mutane takwas.
Saipov, mai shekaru 30, an yi zargin cewa ya yi amfani da motar haya ta Home Depot don kai hari a hanyar keke a West Side Highway, a Lower Manhattan kuma ya buge masu tafiya da masu hawan keke a lokacin tafiya a watan Oktoba.
Don tabbatar da hukuncin kisa, masu gabatar da kara dole ne su nuna cewa Saipov ya kashe duk wadanda aka kashe "da gangan" kuma "da gangan" ya haifar da mummunan rauni, a cewar sanarwar niyyar neman hukuncin kisa da aka gabatar a gundumar kudu ta New York.
Dukkanin laifuffukan biyu na iya jawo hukuncin kisa, a cewar takardar kotun.
Makonni bayan harin, wata babbar kotun tarayya ta kai wa Saipov hari tare da tuhumar da ta yi wa laifin laifuffuka 22 da suka hada da laifuka takwas na kisan kai don amfanin aikata laifuka, wanda masu gabatar da kara na tarayya ke amfani da su a lokuta na mafia, ban da wani laifi na tashin hankali da lalata motoci.
Masu gabatar da kara sun ce harin ya bukaci "tsari da kuma tunanin da ya dace" kuma sun bayyana yadda Saipov ya yi aiki a matsayin "mara kyau, mummunan aiki da lalata".
"Sayfullo Habibullaevic Saipov ya haifar da rauni, lalacewa da asarar dangi da abokai na Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Ann-Laure Decadt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erlij, Hernan Ferruchi, Hernan Diego Mendoza da Alejandro Damian Pagnucco", a cewar sanarwar da aka yi.
Biyar daga cikin wadanda aka kashe 'yan yawon bude ido ne daga Argentina.
Shekaru goma kenan da shari'ar hukuncin kisa ta fara a gundumar kudu ta birnin New York.
An yanke wa wanda ake tuhuma, Khalid Barnes, hukuncin kisa kan wasu 'yan dillalan miyagun kwayoyi biyu, amma daga bisani aka yanke masa hukuncin daurin rai da rai a watan Satumbar 2009.
Lokaci na ƙarshe da aka zartar da hukuncin kisa a cikin wani shari'ar tarayya a New York shine a shekara ta 1953 ga Julius da Ethel Rosenberg, ma'aurata da aka kashe bayan an yanke musu hukuncin kisa saboda yin tawaye don aiwatar da ayyukan leken asiri ga Tarayyar Soviet a lokacin Cold War shekaru biyu da suka gabata.
Dukansu Rosenbergs sun mutu a kujera ta lantarki a ranar 19 ga Yuni, 1953.
A cewar takardun kotun, Saipov, dan asalin Uzbekistan, bai nuna nadama ba a cikin kwanaki da watanni bayan harin.
'Yan sanda sun bayyana cewa ya gaya wa masu binciken cewa yana jin daɗi game da abin da ya yi.
A cewar takardar tuhumar, Saipov ya bayyana wa hukumomi cewa an yi wahayi zuwa gare shi don kai harin bayan ya kalli bidiyon ISIS a wayarsa.
A cewar 'yan sanda, ya kuma nemi a nuna tutar ISIS a dakin asibitin da yake.
Ya ce ba shi da laifi a kan zargin aikata laifuffuka 22.
David Patton, daya daga cikin lauyoyin tarayya da ke wakiltar Saipov, ya ce sun kasance "masu takaici" game da shawarar da ake tuhuma.
"Mun yi la'akari da cewa yanke shawarar neman hukuncin kisa, maimakon karɓar hukuncin kisa da ɗaurin rai ba tare da yiwuwar 'yanci ba zai ƙara tsawaita cutar da waɗannan abubuwan da suka faru ga duk waɗanda ke da hannu", in ji Patton.
Kungiyar kare Saipov ta bukaci masu gabatar da kara da kada su nemi hukuncin kisa.
Wani dan majalisa na jam'iyyar Conservative ya ce ya kamata a sa Nigel Farage a kan batun tattaunawar Brexit
Nigel Farage ya yi alkawarin "daukar da sojojin jama'a" a yau yayin zanga-zangar a taron jam'iyyar Conservative.
Tsohon shugaban jam'iyyar UKIP ya ce 'yan siyasa su "ji matsin lamba daga masu shakka" lokacin da wani dan majalisa na Theresa May ya nuna cewa ya kamata ya jagoranci tattaunawar da EU.
Dan majalisa mai ra'ayin mazan jiya Peter Bone ya fadawa taron Birmingham cewa Birtaniya za ta kasance a waje da EU idan Mr Farage ya zama sakataren Brexit.
Amma kalubalen da Mrs May ke fuskanta wajen sasantawa tsakanin bangarorin da suka rabu ya bayyana lokacin da 'yan Conservative masu goyon bayan hadin kai suka fito don wani zanga-zangar Brexit a The City.
Firaministan kasar na fama da kariya daga tsarin yarjejeniyar Chequers a yayin da masu goyon bayan Brexit, masu goyon bayan EU da EU ke kai hare-hare.
Allies sun nace cewa zai iya cimma yarjejeniya tare da Brussels duk da martani mara kyau kuma suna matsawa masu shakka da kuma jam'iyyar Conservative don zaɓar tsakanin kunshin su da hargitsi.
Mista Bone ya gaya wa taron 'Leave Means Leave' na Solihull cewa yana son ya warware yarjejeniyar Chequers.
Ya ba da shawarar cewa ya kamata a nada Mista Farage a matsayin memba na Majalisar Lords kuma ya kamata a ba shi alhakin tattaunawa da Brussels.
'Idan ya kasance a cikin iko, za mu kasance a yanzu kashe,' ya ce.
Dan majalisa Wellingborough ya kara da cewa: "Zan goyi bayan Brexit, amma dole ne mu warware yarjejeniyar Chequers".
Don bayyana adawarsa ga EU, ya kara da cewa: "Ba mu yi yaƙe-yaƙe na duniya don zama masu bauta ba.
Muna son mu kafa dokokinmu a kasarmu".
Mista Bone ya yi watsi da shawarwarin da ke cewa ra'ayin jama'a ya canza tun lokacin zaben 2016: "Ganin cewa mutanen Burtaniya sun canza tunaninsu kuma suna son zama a can ba gaskiya bane".
Mai goyon bayan Brexit Andrea Jenkyns ta halarci gangamin kuma ta shaida wa manema labarai cewa: "Ina gaya muku ne, firaminista, ku saurari mutane".
"Aikin Chequers ba shi da kyau a tsakanin jama'a, 'yan adawa ba za su goyi bayansa ba, ba shi da kyau a cikin jam'iyyarmu da masu fafutukarmu, waɗanda su ne mutanen da suka fito kan titi kuma suka sa mu lashe zabe.
Ka daina yin alkawarin da kake yi da 'yan wasa kuma ka soma saurarawa".
A wata wasika da ya aika wa Mrs May, ya kara da cewa: "Firai ministoci suna cika aikinsu idan suka cika alkawuransu".
Mr Farage ya ce 'yan siyasa a taron suna bukatar jin matsin lamba idan suna son su yi watsi da shawarar da aka yanke a zaben raba gardama na 2016.
"Wannan, yanzu, batun amana ne tsakanin mu (mutane) da kuma tsarin siyasarmu", in ji shi.
"Suna kokarin cin amanar Brexit kuma a yau muna nan don gaya musu cewa ba za mu bari su yi hakan ba".
A wani sako da ya aika wa taron masu farin ciki, ya kara da cewa: "Ina so ku sa 'yan siyasa, da ke shirin cin amanar Brexit, su ji matsin lamba".
"Muna tattara sojojin kasar nan da suka ba mu nasara a Brexit kuma ba za mu huta ba har sai mun zama Birtaniya mai zaman kanta, mai zaman kanta da alfahari".
A halin yanzu, magoya bayan ƙungiyar sun yi tafiya a Birmingham kafin su gudanar da taron sa'o'i biyu a tsakiyar birnin.
