China ta yi alkawarin kwace Amurka kuma ba zai yiwu tattalin arzikin duniya na biyu ya koma baya ba da jimawa ba.
Don a mayar da Washington baya yana nufin cewa za ta yi watsi da wasu buƙatun, amma yin biyayya ga Amurka a fili zai zama abin kunya ga Xi Jinping, shugaban kasar Sin.
Duk da haka, masana sun ce idan Beijing ta yi wasa da katunan ta yadda ya kamata, matsin lamba daga yakin cinikayya da Amurka na iya amfanar China a cikin dogon lokaci ta hanyar rage dogaro da tattalin arzikin biyu.
"Yadda wani yanke shawara na siyasa a Washington ko Beijing zai iya haifar da yanayin da zai fara rushewa a kowanne daga cikin waɗannan ƙasashe ya fi haɗari fiye da yadda shaidu suka yi tsammani", in ji Abigail Grace, wata mai bincike da ke da alhakin Asiya a Cibiyar New American Security, wata ƙungiyar masana.
