Rahoton da Hukumar Kifi da Dairy ta Florida ta bayar ya nuna cewa an samu raguwar yawan ruwan teku a wasu yankunan da ke yankin Tampa Bay.
A cewar FWC, ana ba da rahoton yanayin yaduwar wurare da yawa a yankunan Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Charlotte da Collier, wanda ke nuna ƙananan taro.
Yawan ruwan teku mai ruwan sama yana da nisan kilomita 200 daga bakin teku, daga arewacin Pinellas zuwa kudancin Lee.
Ana iya samun tabo a cikin kilomita 10 daga gabar tekun Hillsborough County, amma a wurare da yawa fiye da makon da ya gabata.
An kuma lura da ruwan ja a cikin gundumar Pasco.
An ba da rahoton matsakaitan raƙuman ruwa a bakin teku ko nesa da bakin teku a cikin gundumar Pinellas a cikin makon da ya gabata, ƙananan raƙuman ruwa zuwa manyan raƙuman ruwa a gundumar Hillsborough, ƙananan raƙuman ruwa ko manyan raƙuman ruwa a gundumar Manatee, matsakaitan raƙuman ruwa zuwa tsakiyar raƙuman ruwa a gundumar Charlotte, ƙananan raƙuman ruwa a cikin gundumar Lee da ƙananan raƙuman ruwa a gundumar Collier.
Ana ci gaba da samun rahoton ciwon numfashi a Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Lee da Collier.
Babu wani ciwon numfashi da aka samu a cikin makon da ya gabata a arewa maso gabashin Florida.
